{"product_id": "33230", "page": 5, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2018-01-24", "text": "Assassin's Creed II is a particularly interesting game that highlights the coming of age for the main character, Ezio. The PC controls take time to get used too, but you will adapt. The missions are decent, sometimes repetitive. As for the graphics, this game hasn't exactly aged well. That being said, you're going to want to play this game for the story and the main character as it's quite good. Can't wait to see where Brotherhood and Revelations lead me.", "hours": 29.0, "user_id": "76561198148936554", "username": "The_Grand_Jenkins", "products": 50, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 5, "page_order": 7, "recommended": false, "date": "2018-01-24", "text": "I'm copying the review I've made for AC2 Brotherhood, removing some parts specific to that game, because what I've said there applies to this game as well.\n--\nI wanted to do all AC games before reviewing any, I've skipped the whole series and always felt that, given how long has it gone for, it deserved to be played, even though the premise never looked all that promising to me. I've reached this game and had enough, this games don't really deserve all the hype they been getting all these years.\nI've probably gonna keep going just to see it through, to analyze the whole series like a piece of gaming history that at least deserves that, to understand how is it that the AAA gaming industry has today reached so low standards. But if you're wondering: should I buy this game or any of its series?\nDON'T! ASSASSIN'S CREED IS CRAP\nControls suck. Immersion is totally destroyed by this. Parkour puzzles are simple and straightforward, no challenge at all if it wasn't by the character randomly not responding as expected. Freerunning should be the main way of travelling in game, but it rapidly becomes frustating enough to just choose to just walk or run like a normal person.\nThe combat system is too stupid, every enemy has a specific tecnique they're weak to, there's no skill involved, no finesse, no acrobatics, no use of the enviroment, enemies don't adapt to your tactics and it all becomes boring too fast.\nStealth mechanics are the same, just a repetition of the same set of simple challenges over and over.\nThe story is very poor, characters are flat and their voice acting is just plain stereotyped and racist. There's no real story progression up till the very end of the game, because there's no real story to tell, just a bunch of nonsense conspiracy theory that you would find in a creepypasta.\nAnd all those colectibles, challenges and side missions are pointless, pointless as in there's no actual value in them, no reason to do them, they are not fun, they don't really add nothing to the storytelling, just more useless grind.", "hours": 26.7, "username": "War Wizard", "products": 1002, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 5, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2018-01-23", "text": "By far my favorite Assassin's Creed game. I recommend this game and the two after, Brotherhood and Revelations.", "hours": 19.5, "username": "Pyrineer", "products": 156, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 5, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2018-01-23", "text": "\u00d6ncelikle belirtmem gerekir ki oyundaki t\u0131rmanma mekanikleri berbat,3. oyunu 4 kez %100 olarak bitirebilmi\u015ftim ama bu oyunda bunun imkan\u0131 yok gibi.Oyunda fast travel dedi\u011fimiz olay yok o y\u00fczden ordan oraya y\u00fcr\u00fcyerek ya da \u015fehir kap\u0131s\u0131n\u0131n d\u0131\u015f\u0131nda para kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131 di\u011fer \u015fehirlere gitti\u011fimiz yerler var \u00f6rnek olarak son g\u00f6revde Codex Page'leri toplamam\u0131z gerekiyor ve bu Codex'ler toplam 30 tane olarak \u015fehirlere da\u011f\u0131t\u0131lm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r baz\u0131 \u015fehirlerde Codex'ler i\u00e7in haritan\u0131n \u00f6b\u00fcr taraf\u0131na gitmek gerekiyor burdan \u00e7\u0131karmam\u0131z gereken \u015fey ise b\u00f6lgesel \u0131\u015f\u0131nlanma yok.D\u00f6v\u00fc\u015f mekanikleri oyunun ilk ba\u015flar\u0131nda s\u0131k\u0131c\u0131 geliyor ama sonraki b\u00f6l\u00fcmlerde silah ve b\u0131\u00e7a\u011f\u0131m\u0131z oldu\u011fu i\u00e7in hi\u00e7 d\u00f6v\u00fc\u015fe girmeden onlar\u0131 \u00f6ld\u00fcr\u00fcyordum.Bu oyunda Assassin Contract ad\u0131n\u0131 verdi\u011fimiz yan g\u00f6revimsi g\u00f6revlerde var bu Contract'larda eski assassinlerin mezarlar\u0131n\u0131 a\u00e7\u0131p (yuvarlak bir \u015fey al\u0131yoruz bende bilmiyorum)Altair'in Z\u0131rh\u0131'n\u0131 a\u00e7\u0131yoruz,g\u00fczel g\u00f6r\u00fcn\u00fcyor ama ben a\u00e7maya \u00fc\u015fendim.Oyun oynamay\u0131 bildi\u011finiz s\u00fcrece g\u00f6revleri tekte ge\u00e7ebilirsiniz.Oyunun senaryosunu ben 20 saatte bitirdim assassin contractlar\u0131 falan yaparsam muhtemelen 50 saate kadar gidebiliriz.Sab\u0131rs\u0131z biriyseniz ve ''ben direkt dalmay\u0131 severim moruk'' diyorsan\u0131z bu oyunu almay\u0131n.Ama bana g\u00f6re oyun tek kelime ile muhte\u015fem\u00f6tesigalaksideoynad\u0131\u011f\u0131meniyiassassinscreedoyunu.\u0130Y\u0130 FORUMLAR", "hours": 21.8, "username": "MasterSubarashii", "products": 56, "early_access": false}
