{"product_id": "33230", "page": 9, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2018-01-08", "text": "Well, basically it was a story of another Assassin named Ezio. Yeah, I liked the story. Gameplay wasn't repeatetive like the previous one. Never felt boring to be honest. There was enough variety and twist in the gameplay. The control was a bit disturbing while playing with gamepad. Will not explain or summerize the story as I think, you should play to understand the deepness of the story. Won't long the review. Looking forward to play the next Assasin's Creed game.\nHighly recommend this game if you are Assassin's Creed fan or a rich story lover. Overall rating: 8/10", "hours": 23.1, "username": "Magneto_Ratul", "products": 95, "early_access": false}
