{"product_id": "33230", "page": 9, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2018-01-06", "text": "Horrible And Overly Complicated Controls For Keyboard's Users, But As Long As You Have A Controller (Like Logitech Or Xbox, Especially Xbox 360) It Is A Great Game And Fun To Play.\nThe Story's Not Just Good But It's GREAT. Ubisoft Use A Simple Matter And Make It Into A Great Story About Family, Revenge, And Vengeance.\nOverall, It Is A Great Game With Controller, But Not With Keyboard.\nI'd say...... BUY IT!!!\nOne Of The Cheapest, Yet The Best Game In The Series. Yes, I DO MEAN IT.\nOne More Thing. Before You Play This Game. Just Create An Uplay Account Cause If You Don't Activate The Game Code For Uplay, YOU CAN'T PLAY THE GAME.\nIT'S-A-ME MARIO!!", "hours": 6.3, "user_id": "76561198388830329", "username": "Skinny_Sock  / BookSeed", "products": 84, "early_access": false}
