{"product_id": "33230", "page": 10, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2018-01-04", "text": "\"I did not choose this path. It was chosen for me. At first, I thought vengeance would be easy. For thirty years I've lived in the shadows, visited death upon those who deserved it, and vanished like the wind. I don't know who started this conspiracy, but I know who will end it. My name is Ezio Auditore da Firenze. Like my father before me, I am an Assassin.\"\n\u2015Ezio Auditore da Firenze", "hours": 25.2, "username": "Khaled", "products": 761, "early_access": false}
