{"product_id": "33230", "page": 15, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-12-25", "text": "Eaisly the best Assassins Creed game, and Brotherhood with Revealations just steps behind it.\nBasically the whole Ezio chapter is the best part of the Assassins Creed imho.\nI still remember when Multiplayer was announced for Brotherhood, oh the hype. And now? Now we have a \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665, broken on release boring\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665games that are trailing missions with no good story, and \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 face animations ( Black Flag ).", "hours": 5.9, "username": "\u300eT\u2642m\u300f \u02d9\u035c >\u02d9", "products": 424, "early_access": false}
