{"product_id": "33230", "page": 16, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-12-21", "text": "Hands down the best Assassin's Creed game ever... i mean Orgins can be good (i haven't played it) Even if it is better i will still love Ezio and to be honest i think he is probably one of the best characters in any game. His character developement is just magnificent! It's a shame we don't have games like these anymore.. but hey what do i know. Anyways the story is really good, the graphics are still decent and if you  want to feel like a badass, play this masterpiece! The Music too is legendary!!\nOne issue i do have on the pc version however is the controls for the mouse and keyboard, i couldn't get used to them... so if you want to play this game play it with a controller as i think it was intended for this game.", "hours": 7.5, "username": "Btheking", "products": 280, "early_access": false}
