{"product_id": "33230", "page": 21, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-11-29", "text": "I loved the 1st AC. But this one is an all new level of amazing. The plot is absolutly emersive. The graphics are stunning for 2010 standards. All in all, i am now completly in love with the AC series. I have already started AC Brotherhood when i was writing this and i see the story really ties up. Ezio is a very complete character, and his world is stunning. The end of the game is awsome and gets you really hooked up to the saga. Awsome game!\nPS: Took me 25h to finish this campaign including side missions. But if wasn't on a \"road to Origins\" i guess it could be stretched to some solid 35h.\ni recomend you to not only buy this, but di has i did, buy them all!", "hours": 25.2, "username": "Jeff", "products": 261, "found_funny": 2, "early_access": false}
