{"product_id": "33230", "page": 21, "page_order": 6, "recommended": false, "date": "2017-11-29", "text": "Such disappointment.\nI was excited to play through this serie and had amazing experience with the first one with minor issues with the controlling but this one.. is more then pain in the butt control-wise.\nFirst of all it does not register and also not support controller. I tried six billion suggestion to fix that, but nothing worked to by pass that. Already frustrated decided to stick with K&M just to figure out that it doesn't lock the cursor and even program can't lock it so it just keeps alt-tab for me every now and then.\nThe game could be amazing - this port just not let me get to the point to enjoy it. Like at all. Pure pain and suffering and zero gameplay experience.\nI just hope my friend can play this from my account so at least I can see the story. Whatever.\nDon't buy if you have dual monitors. Unless you willing to disable the secondary everytime you launch the game.", "hours": 67.7, "username": "Swevenfox", "products": 218, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
