{"product_id": "33230", "page": 27, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-11-22", "text": "Assassins creed 2 is an outstanding game. it is considered by many to be the best game in the series. it is a great starting point if you want to play assassins creed because well, the first one was alright and if you play the newer ones it makes this game feel empty with less features. this is a must play", "hours": 43.2, "username": "FloiFlob", "products": 254, "early_access": false}
