{"product_id": "33230", "page": 28, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-11-22", "text": "I love the Ezio series of games in the Assassin's Creed franchise. I always find myself coming back to them and sharing them with friends. I've had a couple friends play through the game on my account.\nI highly recommend this game when people ask about Assassin's Creed. There really isn't anything I hate in this one.", "hours": 132.5, "username": "Patchy", "products": 115, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 28, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-11-22", "text": "In my humble opinion this is one of the best Assassin creed, if not maybe the best, everything about this game is excellent, excellent story, excellent graphics, excellent puzzles, excellent characters, and the list goes on.\nYou get to play as Ezio Auditore, who was born in the city of Florence in Italy, walk in the footsteps of some of the greatest minds of renaissance Italy, such as Leonardo da vinci, the Medicis family, you get to witness first hand the struggle for power between the pope and the various Italian families that made their fortunes from trading spice and silk with the Ottoman empire and visit all those amazing cities such as Florence and Venise, all renderd with a lot of attention to detail and historical exactitude, truly an Amazing experience.", "hours": 27.7, "user_id": "76561198027179912", "username": "Rimka", "products": 235, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 28, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-11-22", "text": "After 10 years and 35 hrs in game I finished the 1st assassins creed .only after I installed AC2 and started playing it .I found a new hope in finishing the first one .everything i didnt know i didn't like about 1st one was better in AC2. like all but the last  part of that 10 years was spent in Masyaf on the pick pocket mission granted it wasn't constant playing that whole time.\nIt took AC2 to give me the will to finish it. with some reconfiguring of the controls to  make it easier to play i finished it. now i'm deep in to Ac2 and loving every minute.and can't wait to finish to play the others  working up to Orgins.", "hours": 68.4, "username": "Goldendude", "products": 369, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 28, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-11-22", "text": "The AC 2 trilogy was by far the high point in the AC lineup. AC 3 was ok. It all goes downhill from there.", "hours": 28.1, "user_id": "76561197960510243", "username": "Nabbun", "products": 75, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 28, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-11-22", "text": "Amazing.  It's old, it's clunky, it's rough, but it's amazing.  The graphics are still nice.  The combat is better then Syndicate's tbh.  And Italy.  Let's just say you can't miss this one.", "hours": 13.2, "user_id": "76561198032740018", "username": "jhchu84", "products": 67, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 28, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-11-22", "text": "1st of all , I would like to mention that this game improves upon its predecessor in term of graphics , gameplay , open world exploration , loots , side quest , character customisation , upgrades , visual upgrades.\nThe story is flawless , fun , brutal , saddening at times.\nHad a lot of fun while playing it.\nI guess , its best played with controller but then u need to customise the control as the defaults r bit wierd.\nJust match the color code with buttons on ur xbox360/one controller. Works fine with the bluetooth of XBOX One S controller.\nIt would have been great if this game had 'Steam Achievements' but it does not but then again the game itself compensates it.", "hours": 20.9, "user_id": "76561198168575902", "username": "ayushrajrules", "products": 60, "early_access": false}
