{"product_id": "33230", "page": 28, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-11-22", "text": "Assassins Creed 2 is on of the best games i\u2019ve played from the series. The combat isn\u2019t the best, but you feel immersed. The story is amazing and takes you all over Italy set during the renaissance. I got to 100% and enjoyed every moment of it.", "hours": 32.0, "username": "Neotric27 \u271f \u0639\u064a\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0633\u0631", "products": 65, "early_access": false}
