{"product_id": "33230", "page": 32, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-11-12", "text": "Assassin's Creed 2 is very nice game.\nCan easily get lost in it with it's open world and freedom to do things. There are many places to explore and story is super long. World is quite huge. Has many varieties in assassinating and in compat ways. There is upgradeable gear system which I really enjoyed. Specially the dye changes in different cities - customization plays always big roll for me.\nAssassin's Creed 2 was many times better than first game. Eventho it was better you still should play AC I first due to story connection.\nI recommend the game but only if have played AC I first - story will make much more sense.\nxTzharkz [Eric].", "hours": 35.6, "username": "xTzharkz", "products": 50, "early_access": false}
