{"product_id": "33230", "page": 35, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-11-04", "text": "A really good story with cool timeline, and long. The ending to the story is such a cliff hanger and can't wait to play the next one. Has a decent open world size for the age of the game. It's intresting to run around and climb buildings for those who are into it, not to many side quests but there's enough. Works great and didn't run into any issues with the game.", "hours": 22.5, "user_id": "76561198063604502", "username": "VaultMobster", "products": 76, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
