{"product_id": "33230", "page": 39, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-10-15", "text": "The incredible amount of improvements made over the first AC game are so extensive it is not even funny. Parkour is still a bit buggy but drastically improved.\nThe major negatives are an annoying heavy blur/gloom filter on everything, espically distant objects. Also sword sound effects have a permanent wet sounding echo to them, that yes, should exist in certain situations, but is way overdone in this game. Sword fighting outdoors does not cause such a deep reverb eco.\nOverall tho a decent game compared to the original. This game is weaker when held up against newer AC games.", "hours": 22.7, "username": "patzivota", "products": 96, "early_access": false}
