{"product_id": "33230", "page": 44, "page_order": 7, "recommended": false, "date": "2017-09-30", "text": "If this is the best the AC series have to offer (according to fans), i finally know what Trump did with his loan of a million dollar.\nCons-\nThe controls are made by monkeys, for monkeys.\nThe optimisation was done by me one random night when i was wasted on liquor.\nThe amount of glitches in this game make my life look like perfection.\nPros-\nHaving a large amount of freedom to approach each mission is pretty nice\nAssassinations are pretty satisfying\nOverall: 4/10\nAlso, im gonna suggest a new death sentence to my local law enforcers, Death by using Ubisoft DRM. I can still faintly hear my computer crying for help against this monster", "hours": 9.8, "username": "IDGAFOS", "products": 175, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
