{"product_id": "33230", "page": 70, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-06-16", "text": "Undoubtebly the best assassin's creed game ever produced\nIts got the best storyline in all of the games, the missions are fun\nTheres lots of diversity in missions types\ntheres the classic parkour element of all assassins creed products\nThis game is still extremely stunning even though its old\nIf you have the money and are getting into assassin's creed get this game\nEzio is a \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 slayer too, the chicks dig him", "hours": 15.9, "username": "Oblivion.", "products": 32, "early_access": false}
