{"product_id": "33230", "page": 70, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-06-15", "text": "Assassin's Creed II is a very special game for me.It is the first AC game I played\uff0cand it was exactly the game that made me love Ubisoft.The story,the parkour,the music,the city and the imagination of it made me feel like that it was the type of 3A I've been looking forward to play.\nGlad to see Assassin's Creed Origins being announced at E3. Fortunately the ancient Egypt is a perfect theme for Assassin's Creed.I hope we will see great chages in it.", "hours": 31.0, "username": "Unthinkable_43", "products": 176, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 70, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-06-14", "text": "Probably the best story of any Assassins Creed game. The gameplay and graphics don't seem outdated to me. But some of the bugs are enfuriating! One time I got stuck between a ladder and a wall and had to wait while I was helplessly slashed to death. Still worth it though if you pick it up on sale.", "hours": 67.9, "user_id": "76561198143172504", "username": "Mush_Murphy", "products": 116, "early_access": false}
