{"product_id": "33230", "page": 72, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-06-07", "text": "It was absolutely fantastic. Excelent gameplay, good story, so much to do in any moment.\nA vast improvement from Assassin's Creed 1. Better combat, story, controls,same camera, same problems with Ezio climbing walls you don't want to because...controller, same \"Get every viewpoint\" obsession, same badass killing blade(s), better game economy, shops, not repeating same stuff 9 times....I should stop now.\nCan't go wrong buying the game, especially on sale(then it's a no brainer)!!\n9.5/10", "hours": 21.9, "user_id": "76561198061836481", "username": "Exerdath", "products": 229, "found_funny": 5, "early_access": false}
