{"product_id": "33230", "page": 75, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-05-23", "text": "AC2 is a gold sequel to the first game, improving everything from it, including: AI, gameplay mechanics, you don't do the same thing in every mission, the storyline and side-quests are really well made, eagle vision is much better, animus doesn't have the glitch which made Altair die when trying to swim, there are not drunk people that push only you!, they added weapon, armor, etc. shops that wasn't present in the 1st game and last the in-game music is really good. I play it even in 2017 and I like it because it brings the player the experience of a true AC game.", "hours": 50.0, "username": "Kominops", "products": 70, "early_access": false}
