{"product_id": "33230", "page": 76, "page_order": 8, "recommended": false, "date": "2017-05-08", "text": "I bought this game because of how much I loved ezio's character. But in stead I got a game that doesn't even work, I would open the game and it would just say updating, updating \"sorry but ubisoft severs are down come back later\" so I would come back later, in my case the next day just for it to tell me the same thing this is why I think I wasted my money and I don't think others should get it", "hours": 7.0, "user_id": "76561198028622759", "username": "Scrapy", "products": 12, "early_access": false}
