{"product_id": "33230", "page": 77, "page_order": 0, "recommended": false, "date": "2017-05-07", "text": "Something is wrong with this game when it comes to saving.  Ive lost data twice over the weekend.  Uplay or Steam needs a better cloud cause Im able to do it with any other game besides this PoS.  Extreme\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665that I wasted money and time just to play a game from the start everytime I play it. Last time I buy something from steam, can't even trust it to make a local save either.", "hours": 0.7, "username": "The_Unseen_Shot", "products": 37, "early_access": false}
