{"product_id": "33230", "page": 83, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-04-10", "text": "An awesome game. Everything about it is an improvement on the first installment. ACII is up alongside Arkham City, Tomb Raider, Gears of War, GTAV and God of War when it comes to great 3rd person games. It takes everything that was good about the first Assassin's Creed and improves on it. Then it get's rid of everthing rubbish about it's predecessor and replaces it with fun side quests and varying gamepaly.\nIf you like 3rd person games, you need to buy ACII. Don't wait for it to be on sale.\n9/10", "hours": 142.4, "user_id": "76561198168661351", "username": "isbadiz", "products": 100, "early_access": false}
