{"product_id": "33230", "page": 86, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-03-30", "text": "Its my honest opinion the Original Assassins creed games are the backbone of what stealth games are today. The franchise as a whole but mainly the earlier titles, laid the foundation for such a large and widely growing fanbase for the stealth genre we have today. Assassins creed is a must play game for any stealth fanatics showing off massive upgrades to its father title named 'Assassins Creed'. Assassins Creed 2 promotes richer storyline with an immersive gameplay if you're in the right mindset.  Honestly my favourite franchise of games ever created , moulding my taste of games and what I now like today 10/10", "hours": 28.1, "username": "Hop3less", "products": 118, "early_access": false}
