{"product_id": "33230", "page": 88, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-03-26", "text": "It was the first and last Assassin's Creed game that added something new that made it worth to play. Having played the first, third, fourth... and then I don't know how many f***ing games they made but Black Flag & AC3 as well. Going off track, but for me this game was the first and last Assassin's Creed game ever made.\nIf you liked the never Assassin's Creed games, good on you, you have sh!t taste in video games.\nIf you have not played any Assassin'c Creed games ever, buy this off or on sale I don't really care. It really is worth playing.", "hours": 16.0, "user_id": "76561198069296497", "username": "ment0r Cx", "products": 96, "early_access": false}
