{"product_id": "33230", "page": 89, "page_order": 4, "recommended": false, "date": "2017-03-25", "text": "I think this is my favourite game ever. So much story, features, improvement on the last,\nBut one word. It will be the most common word in the negative reviews section. And its that \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665t  that comes with every Assassin's creed game. It is resovled when pirating the game but its main aim to stop pirating.\nAlso it took me like half an hour to start this thing with first time set-up, load in UdontPLAY, (even worse if its not installed yet), 2 different permission accepts and a password enter, and then finding my UdontPLAY password/account.\nALSO YOU CANT REPLAY MEMORIES!!!", "hours": 4.0, "user_id": "76561198164082793", "username": "\"Lets try Communism again\"", "products": 88, "early_access": false}
