{"product_id": "33230", "page": 92, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-03-15", "text": "This game is by far the greatest assassin's creed game EVER!\nWhen I compare this to the new ac games like unity and rogue I think, I don't need these new \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665t Mechanics, I only need the classics and I'm good. Ezio Auditore Da Firenze is the best Assassin who does the most insane\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\nOverall this game is a LEGEND!!!\n-Aphlore", "hours": 38.8, "username": "Aphlore", "products": 105, "early_access": false}
