{"product_id": "33230", "page": 102, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-01-27", "text": "I have spent more time than I care to admit playing this game, and I will likely spend more time playing it in the future. I have always loved historical events, and Assassin's Creed II is directly up that alley. I consider this game to be wonderfully written, and while it is certainly not perfect, it is one of the better games that I have played, in my opinion.\nThough one should usually begin at the beginning, I would consider this game a good place to start if you're trying to get into Assassin's Creed (it's what I did, after all).", "hours": 133.4, "user_id": "76561198068213971", "username": "SandSquid16", "products": 135, "early_access": false}
