{"product_id": "33230", "page": 112, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-01-03", "text": "First chapter following Ezio Auditore's story. Love the open world of the geometrically accurate Renaissance Italy. Fascinating plot intertwined with world history.\nWe work in the dark to serve the light.", "hours": 19.2, "username": "Jet", "products": 33, "early_access": false}
