{"product_id": "33230", "page": 112, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-01-02", "text": "I've played through most of the Assassin's Creed games, and this is definitely my favorite.  They improved upon the first game in almost every way.  Ezio is a likeable character, and I loved how they wove the Renaissance history into the game.  It's incredible to climb up iconic Renaissance buildings like the Florence Cathedral.", "hours": 49.2, "user_id": "76561197971885160", "username": "chewy119", "products": 729, "early_access": false}
