{"product_id": "33230", "page": 113, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-12-31", "text": "Really fun game for alternate history buffs.\nGameplay - 8/10 (Challenging and not as simple as future entries.)\nGraphics - 7/10 (Hold up really well almost 10 years later, although a little blocky on closeup, textures are nothing special.)\nAudio - 10/10\nStory - 10/10 (Best AC story I've yet seen, phenomenal acting and engaging characters.)\nOverall - 9/10 (Great game with only a few shortcomings, glitched out on me only 4-5 times, which is acceptable for any game, because no game can be absolutely perfect.", "hours": 32.1, "username": "Ex Nihilo", "products": 315, "early_access": false}
