{"product_id": "33230", "page": 120, "page_order": 7, "recommended": false, "date": "2016-12-21", "text": "I'm actually VERY disappointed because of this pathetic service. I bought the deluxe CD key a long time ago on a slow desktop I used to have but it's now broken and fried. I have a new laptop and it won't let me use the key on this computer EVEN THOUGH I HAVE THE ACCOUNTS IT WAS USED ON AND PROOF OF PURCHASE. Highly unsatisfied and will NEVER buy another CD key from Uplay ever again. I want the game I purchased back NOW. I am warning everyone reading this, if you buy a game from Uplay, don't get a new computer. Just saying. Uplay is basically a scam/con. (By the way, I bought this key along with a standard AC3 key on steam but it's used for Uplay, I can't use either of them.)", "hours": 1.0, "user_id": "76561198125856130", "username": "BurningOranges", "products": 28, "found_funny": 2, "early_access": false}
