{"product_id": "33230", "page": 122, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-12-17", "text": "This game is like your first love. You were young and didn't really know what you were doing, but it was amazing, fun and exciting; you will never forget it and nothing seems to compare to it; you dream about it every now and then. Sometimes, when another one ends, you even go back to it, to spend another 30 hours of passion, before going back to your normal life ;)", "hours": 33.2, "username": "Ciosty", "products": 81, "early_access": false}
