{"product_id": "33230", "page": 123, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-12-10", "text": "Wait, WTF?!\nActual review:\nOh my god!!! One of the BEST games ever! Golly, what a plot twist!\nStory: 5/5\nGameplay (easy to learn quickly): 4/5\nVisuals (without the Ezio collection): 4/5\nOpen World: 4.5/5\nOverall: 17.5/20\n= 87.5% = B+\nNow I MUST play the other games! Looking forward to the Assassin's Creed movie the 21st this December and the AC: Empire game next year or so!\nP.S. I wish this game had Steam Achievements, but it is completely GREAT without them.", "hours": 66.4, "user_id": "76561198121358136", "username": "Moonstrike", "products": 68, "early_access": false}
