{"product_id": "33230", "page": 131, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-11-27", "text": "\"Nothing is true, everything is permitted. Rest in peace.\" - Ezio Auditore da Firenze\nGood:\n+ Huge open world environment with reactive NPCs\n+ Gripping plot and character development\n+ Good blend of real historical references\n+ Excellent voice acting and soundtrack\n+ Plenty of optional objectives and collectables\n+ Smooth free-running and combat animations\nBad:\n- Easy and straightforward AI\n- Unrealistic ragdoll physics\nScore: 9/10", "hours": 105.4, "user_id": "76561198118856673", "username": "TediousError", "products": 283, "early_access": false}
