{"product_id": "33230", "page": 132, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-11-26", "text": "I've been playing this game for years and years now and not once has it ever felt boring to me. As a huge fan of history, this game blends beautiful landscapes, history, fun gameplay, and a thrilling story in one beautifully crafted masterpiece. Cannot recommend this game enough.", "hours": 0.7, "username": "SoleY", "products": 137, "early_access": false}
