{"product_id": "33230", "page": 155, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-09-10", "text": "Fantastic game. Almost all the negative reviews come from people who can't connect to Uplay. I've personally never failed to connect to Uplay either in this or any other Ubisoft game, but I know some people have problems.\nOne other thing: I definitely recommend playing with a controller because of the wacky keyboard controls; however, there are two files you have to download and paste into the game to get it to work correctly.\nOther than those two potential issues, neither of which bothered me, it's an absolutely great game, right up there with Black Flag, maybe even better. There aren't nearly as many of Black Flag's infamous tail quests (which I wasn't particularly good at). Anyway, grab it on sale.", "hours": 31.6, "username": "Zed Clampet", "products": 605, "early_access": false}
