{"product_id": "33230", "page": 156, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-09-07", "text": "++ Very good, long story\n++ \"Old\" game but still very much playable today\n++ Variety in cities, a lot to explore (72 viewpoints)\n+ Historical information and accuracy\n+ A lot to collect\n+ Renovating Monteriggioni is nice, good incentive to get money\n+ Graphics are very nice but not stunning\n+ Smooth gameplay, sometimes bit awkward\n- No one kill chain combo's\n- Only one enemy attacks at a time\n- No difficulty selection\n- No big fights", "hours": 100.3, "user_id": "76561198048764251", "username": "Boaske", "products": 16, "early_access": false}
