{"product_id": "33230", "page": 159, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-08-15", "text": "For everyone who is whining about UPlay, why not check the community, this is a great game, and most of the reviews are about UPlay. I had the issue also, that's when I found this Guide:\nit's easily fixable, took me 5 minutes. Some people also might have a soundcard issue (audio playing through speakers) and usually a quick restart will do the trick. (And side note, controls are easily changed)\nHopefully this helped and/or encouraged to purchase this fantastic game", "hours": 58.4, "username": "Mysterion", "products": 29, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 159, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-08-15", "text": "A total step up from the first Assassin's Creed. That was a great game, but AC II is even better. It has better controls(which for AC on PC, the controls are already weird but once you figure them out in one game you have an easy time with the rest of the games), better gameplay, more to do outside of the main story line, and it has captions.", "hours": 59.6, "username": "heartofscylla", "products": 37, "early_access": false}
