{"product_id": "33230", "page": 165, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-07-15", "text": "ignore the hour time,i played it a lot and finished the game....\nPROS:\n+Ezio your main character\n+Italy\n+Every city is beautifully detailed\n+All Character is Lovely and Unique\n+LOTS AND LOTS of collectables\n+All of your weapons is useful (and gadgets) during combat,assasination,ETC.\n+Combat is much better and responsive,unlike AC 1\n+The mission are very unique,sometimes........\n+the parkour is well done and better than AC 1 (Obviously....)\n+All of voice acting is superb\n+Not so bad character models\n+NPC's doing their chores,Some of it....\n+Epic Storyline\n+Unexpected Plot & Twist\n+And many,many pros....\nCons:\n-Dumb AI\n-The game is a bit too easy\n-Needed the stealth system in AC unity\n-NPC's can be annoying,when doing missions...\n-When parkour sometimes will get the wrong way like falling from the building and ETC\n-Bugs and a little bit of glitches\n-UPLAY!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n8.5/10 would laugh because of AC 2 Logic......", "hours": 7.8, "username": "Roxortus!", "products": 142, "early_access": false}
