{"product_id": "33230", "page": 170, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-07-01", "text": "What can i say, even so the first AC was a bad and sad excuse for a PoP successor, the Story drove me to AC2 and they Improved the whole Gameplay alot! Just stay away from any DLC and you will have a grand time with a good Story.\nAnd I would recommend a Sale of course.", "hours": 35.8, "user_id": "76561198105010584", "username": "PrinceVinc", "products": 288, "early_access": false}
