{"product_id": "33230", "page": 171, "page_order": 0, "recommended": false, "date": "2016-06-28", "text": "It was OK. After watching Videogamedunkey's review, I didn't want to finish it, but I had already bought 1-4. So now since I know that all the side missions are just repeats I am just going to play the main missions from now on. I only bought the series because of the low prices. It's one of those games that you don't want to play again, but you already bought it.", "hours": 34.6, "user_id": "76561198074850627", "username": "sam.felder", "products": 138, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
