{"product_id": "33230", "page": 171, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-06-26", "text": "I personally prefered the first Assassin's Creed (likely because, unlike most people it seems, I didn't really like the characters and because I enjoyed the setting of the original more), but the sequal is still quite enjoyable. Having more story elements, it also is less repetative than the original.", "hours": 22.0, "username": "JakeOmega", "products": 268, "early_access": false}
