{"product_id": "33230", "page": 172, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-06-24", "text": "The assassin's creed series is very well done.\nThis story follows Ezio Auditore da Firenze and is very fun to play.\nBuy this and the rest.", "hours": 49.4, "username": "dgouk", "products": 257, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 172, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-06-24", "text": "A MASTERPIECE\nI've played all the Assassins Creed's but the story and development of Ezio throughout 2, Brotherhood and Revelations truly makes me cry.\nIt is rare in a game to find yourself so emotionally attached to a character as many are to Ezio. You literally track his story from birth to a young teen to a disciplined master assassin and later, in revelations, the most senior rank of Mentor.\nThis game is truly one of the greatest gems in the entire gaming world, the gameplay, the open world, but most importantly the story, emotions and character development is like no other.\nI salute you Ezio Auditore da Firenze.", "hours": 56.8, "user_id": "76561198263495404", "username": "Godfather3000000000", "products": 55, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 172, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-06-24", "text": "After losing my faith in the franchise due to Unity, buying this game and playing it was like a breath of fresh air and i can say i like Assassin's Creed again", "hours": 58.3, "user_id": "76561198089783072", "username": "Mater", "products": 51, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
