{"product_id": "33230", "page": 200, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-02-22", "text": "That's what I expect of an Assassin Game.\nThe first AC game was a real let down for me... no real story just some random assassinations in seemingly generic cities. I couldn't identify myself with Altair.\nBut Ezio is a whole different story there. You got everything, charming characters you get to like or dislike, a really large challenging universe with a background which has its twists and way way to many collectibles.\nCompletiontime about 25 hours with most side quests and challenges done.", "hours": 25.4, "username": "Astore", "products": 664, "early_access": false}
