{"product_id": "33230", "page": 206, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-01-31", "text": "I'm comparing this to the first assassin's creed.\nHere's the pros/cons.\nPros: - better graphic than the first one\n- ez combat system\n- ez getting alot of money\n- subtitles\n- hidden gun\n- FLYING\n- No more over suspicious npc, now they think i'm an entertainer or a desperate lover\nOkay: - the free run system can be annoying but can be helpful too\n- the button pressing in a scene are too fast. But it doesn't matter anyway\nCons: - Horses still can't get into the city\n- Can't fast travel in the same city\n- smoke bomb pouch are too small\n- symbols hud got really confusing sometimes\nOverall obviously better than AC 1,\nI give it 9/10", "hours": 60.2, "user_id": "76561198122658108", "username": "HijackLoL", "products": 282, "early_access": false}
