{"product_id": "33230", "page": 219, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-12-29", "text": "Since i have a 3GB Ram PC im going to have to make this review UNIVERSAL since i played this game on Xbox 360 and PS3\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nNow...I love First Person games. Hell, Half the games i play are first person puzzle games, or go around shoot everything you see games. BUT...i never liked 3rd person till i played this. 3rd person was fun when you can watch DOUBLE HIDDEN BLADES go into a guards face. And the templars are \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665s so its satisfying when you kill them. Even a character that is against you at the beginning you kill later in the game! GG\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665", "hours": 5.0, "username": "Cyanide the Emo Squirrel", "products": 120, "early_access": false}
