{"product_id": "33230", "page": 224, "page_order": 2, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-12-18", "text": "I love this game.\nI hate UPlay.", "hours": 39.8, "username": "Pragman86", "products": 299, "found_funny": 64, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 224, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-12-17", "text": "I love sandbox games and this one's a good one.  I recommend it for people who enjoy completionism and sneak games.  I give it an 8/10, for the following reasons:\nPros\n-Multiple ways to complete objectives\n-Side quests and collections have a reason/reward\n-Decent play time\n-Historical figures in a fictional setting\nCons\n-Five forced fights\n-Desmond stuff\n-Can't add to quick menu\n-Hints come with button colors and pictures\n-No firm ending\nI play on PC using keyboard/mouse, and the controls can be set up for shift-sprint like normal, so the port wasn't an issue.  The hints were overcome once you have the pictures memorized, and turning off the HUD removed the controller aspect.\nThe game leads to the sequel and thus feels a bit incomplete main story-wise (the Desmond stuff), but the parts that take place in the past are fulfilled.\nOverall, I would recommend this game.", "hours": 37.5, "user_id": "76561198052554580", "username": "daschus", "products": 123, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 224, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-12-17", "text": "The best AC game made, even now, all these years later. Ezio is simply the best character Ubisoft has ever made. The environment is incredible, Florence, Venice, and the other towns are breath-taking.\nThe graphics have aged wonderfully, better than almost any other games from 2008.\nThe gameplay was at it's best, not too many gadgets and weapons, but not too streamlined either.\n10/10, I've bought this game 3 times and will continue to play it again.", "hours": 59.4, "username": "Arby", "products": 384, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 224, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-12-17", "text": "cool game", "hours": 57.3, "user_id": "76561198207670489", "username": "Kvouth", "products": 9, "early_access": false}
