{"product_id": "33230", "page": 225, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-12-14", "text": "Assassin's Creed II is one of the best in the series and it makes it more enjoyable because it's in Third Person, so there are many places to explore and just basically a free open world  stealth game packed with action. It is set in the 15th and early 16th Cenuturay Renaissance Era~\nIf you download this game you may need to download Ubisoft's Uplay which you can find on there website. It's simple although it took me awhile to figure out, because after installing you get a mesage that Ubisoft's Uplay in not available etc~", "hours": 7.0, "username": "\u300eMILK.PEACH\u300f", "products": 41, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
