{"product_id": "33230", "page": 229, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-11-29", "text": "ACII is a huge improvement over the original with a far more interesting protagonist as well as a great setting. Combat is simplifed to be more fun and less frustrating.", "hours": 32.4, "username": "The Milkman", "products": 689, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 229, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-11-29", "text": "At least when I played it in 2009, I thought it was the best story driven game I've ever played. And it still holds up (2015). I've played this game about 10 times (150+ hours with achievements etc.), I think that speaks for itself.\nWith the free mod/plug-in/program SoftTH, i could play with a resolution of 5280x1080 on my 3 monitors (#PCMasterRace). UPlay isn't as bad as everyone says it is. No problems yet.\nThis is probably the best in the series so far (haven't played Syndicate or Origins yet though).\nMy list of the AC games:\n- II\n- IV: Black Flag\n- Rogue\n- Brotherhood\n- The Original\n- Unity\n- III\n- Revelations", "hours": 17.8, "username": "viON", "products": 205, "early_access": false}
