{"product_id": "33230", "page": 230, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-11-28", "text": "A superior follow-up to the original Assassin's Creed. With added roleplying elements and somehwat simpler combat, it not only expanded, but improved on many aspects that made the original such a solid gaming experience. Yes, there are issues, such as easy to acquire cash and nothing to spend it on, but they are minor, if not slightly regrettable issues.\nWarning: I almost needed three hands to control my avatar during some of the more complex jump puzzles while using a mouse and keyboard. I have a somewhat disabled right hand, therefore using a gaming controller is very difficult for me. That being said, generally speaking, a mouse a keyboard worked just fine.\n9/10", "hours": 74.8, "user_id": "76561197971943763", "username": "Grimhotep", "products": 144, "early_access": false}
