{"product_id": "33230", "page": 234, "page_order": 4, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-11-19", "text": "Can't play the game cause some Ubisoft service is \"unavailable\". (It didn't even state you couldn't play the game offline when buying). Last time I bought a game from Ubisoft, that I never got to play cause of a loading bug, they replied to only one of my many mails; saying since I allready have pressed play, they wouldn't refund allthough it couldn't be played. Ubisoft gets another vote for worst game-company, and I'll have to never play their games again. RIP Heroes of Might and Magic :(\nHehe and funniest part is I can't review it without 5 min playing.... Have to look at \"service unavailable\" screen for another 4 mins...", "hours": 17.2, "user_id": "76561198006315180", "username": "SpikeFeather", "products": 52, "early_access": false}
