{"product_id": "33230", "page": 241, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-10-29", "text": "Sometimes when you are climbing and leaping around Venice, you may end up leaping off the wrong edge, or climbing something you didn't want to climb, but despite that, this is perhaps the best, or one of the best Assassins Creed Games, It has beautiful graphics, well made environments, great gameplay, and an amazing story.\nGraphics:7/10\nGameplay:8/10\nEnvironments:9.5/10\nStory:10/10", "hours": 32.2, "username": "Full DPS Reinhardt", "products": 434, "early_access": false}
