{"product_id": "33230", "page": 242, "page_order": 7, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-10-27", "text": "I bought the game, but after ten or fiteen minutes of trying to log in followed by a few hours of trying to tangle with Ubisofts customer service, I'll just play the game on a console.\nThe developers seem to fear that somebody would actually try to play the game after purchse, so locked it up effectively with U-Play.  It may be a good game, but it isn't on Steam.", "hours": 0.1, "user_id": "76561198034109260", "username": "realpedro", "products": 161, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 242, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-10-27", "text": "really good game!", "hours": 27.1, "username": "ThatGreenGuy", "products": 59, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 242, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-10-27", "text": "Good, solid, polished, interesting game. Solid one.", "hours": 1.0, "user_id": "76561197987350504", "username": "*UTA* SpandauRanger", "products": 42, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 243, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-10-27", "text": "Before I met Ezio, I was bound by rules and supposed truths. This game really was, is, and will be a revolutionary game.\n10/10 on any criteria except for maybe easter eggs (420/mario for that one)\nThe fact that I have run through the story several times and spent an additional 30 hours just exploring alone should prove to most that this is a phenomenal game. Those of you thinking about Ubisoft's recent reputation on the Assassin's creed series should get this just to see why the fan base is really disappointed. But, I think that after a game like this, any fan base would be dissapointed by the next ones in the series.\nI would reccomend this to everyone highly; this and brotherhood.", "hours": 82.7, "username": "Polartrain123", "products": 159, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 243, "page_order": 1, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-10-27", "text": "uplay", "hours": 1.1, "username": "Cloud Pleaser", "products": 47, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 243, "page_order": 2, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-10-26", "text": "Got this on a steam sale ages ago, but never bothered with it because I always heard the Ubisoft games were unplayable garbage hobbled by UPlay.\nFirst time opening, I immediately get a \"server is unavailable\" message. 20 minutes later, still the same thing. Guess I was right.", "hours": 37.7, "user_id": "76561197995108422", "username": "spencer_thomas", "products": 406, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 243, "page_order": 3, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-10-26", "text": "First of all, you usually get moves explained by symbols (foot, left hand, right hand, locked face etc). On a PC this means that at the beginning you will have to switch A LOT to the Key bindings and find out what they mean. BTW. forget to use the mouse in the options menue because this doesnt work at all.....use 2-key and 3-key. I played it on a Playstation and it was pretty smooth, but on it is a total mess......you just feel that it was not meant to be played on PC and the porting is a disaster.", "hours": 15.8, "user_id": "76561197969028658", "username": "Hugh Janeous", "products": 45, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 243, "page_order": 4, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-10-26", "text": "Cant play this game at all!!!!  Keep saying that Ubisoft server is down. Please fix it!", "hours": 44.9, "username": "I Am the Knight", "products": 21, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 243, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-10-26", "text": "Huge open world game, nice story.\nOne of the best in the series.", "hours": 32.0, "username": "Dan The Man", "products": 676, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 243, "page_order": 6, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-10-26", "text": "I would have liked to tell you that the game had an amazing story, relatable characters, etc... But i couldnt even play this game because i couldnt use my keyboard for some reason. I have it on MAC, but i still expected to be able to actually play it", "hours": 0.7, "user_id": "76561198133140773", "username": "Novalion113", "products": 10, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 243, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-10-26", "text": "Haha that's a spicy meatball, Italianoo~", "hours": 21.1, "username": "Whopper King Steve", "products": 151, "early_access": false}
