{"product_id": "33230", "page": 252, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-10-13", "text": "To start off I want to let people know that this game uses uplay and for some people that's a no buy but if you can look past that then you will find yourself playing one of the best games that has ever been released. Truly this is without a doubt the best assassin's creed game that has released or will release the story is honestly fantastic and the gameplay is some of the most enjoyable that I have ever experienced in an assassin's creed game or any other game. I own 3 copies of assassin's creed 2 on ps3 xbox 360 and pc so if that doesn't tell you the game is great I have no idea what can. Do yourself a favor and purchase this game you won't regret it once", "hours": 0.9, "user_id": "76561198041605804", "username": "xldcreflexlx", "products": 209, "early_access": false}
