{"product_id": "33230", "page": 252, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-10-11", "text": "After playing the first game till my fingertips were plain from clicking, there was a relief in playing the secong game in the title.\nAwesome as it is, there is one major drawback \u2013 it is the only game in the series where you can not replay main missions. I would really love to replay some Venice flying or carriage riding along with Leonardo.\nComparing to the previous title, the game added a lot of diversity:\nLoved by many, this is the game you should play to experience the story and progress of an Assassin.", "hours": 33.7, "username": "Hlelia", "products": 72, "early_access": false}
