{"product_id": "33230", "page": 253, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-10-08", "text": "I never understood why this game was so popular and I never understood why people said \"it's the best game in the series\" until I actually brought the game. And holy sh*t what a game this is. For a game that's about 6 years old, it's.... Its just fabulous and couldn't agree more with this being the best (Sorry black flag..)\nThe beginning of the story (Ezios story, no one gives a sh*t about Desmond at this point) had this charm of 2 brothers just being brothers and not alot of the get straight into the action bullsh*t. :D)\nAnd for the rest of what I've played... very sad indeed. SPOILER:\nThe soundtrack is very, very good. Some of the music like the famous \"Ezios family\" are an absolute masterpiece\nScenery? From what I've seen, it's beautiful.\nTo conclude, buy this game now", "hours": 6.3, "username": "\u03bbctionwill65", "products": 143, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
