{"product_id": "33230", "page": 253, "page_order": 7, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-10-04", "text": "Could not get any asscreed game to run on windows 10. Googled around, it's a common problem. Ubisoft does not officially support windows 10.\nThis game installs another launcher (ubisoft launcher), and I believe it requires an internet connection.\nUbisoft is everything wrong with PC gaming. Never giving them another dime.", "hours": 32.5, "username": "Traches", "products": 227, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 253, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-10-04", "text": "I realize that I'm late to the party. Assassin's Creed 2 is an amazing game. You want to be a mideval Batman, this game is the game for you. I'm sure you've seen other review praise this game as well, They are all true. I do want to point out a few issues. The controls are screwed up for game pad controllers. There are fixes to remap the buttons but its pretty sad they you have to hunt down a hack to fixed what should be fixed in game. Also during close quaters combat, often you will be fighting the camera as much as the characters. Still, its a must play game.", "hours": 47.4, "username": "Baron Calamity", "products": 2546, "found_funny": 6, "early_access": false}
