{"product_id": "33230", "page": 257, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-09-09", "text": "Herkes'e merhaba arkada\u015flar Assassin's Creed serisinin nerdeyse b\u00fct\u00fcn oyunlar\u0131n\u0131 oynad\u0131m ama bu zaman\u0131n da yap\u0131lan en iyi oyunlardan bir tanesi tabikide iyi olanlar vard\u0131r elbet ama bana kal\u0131rsa zaman\u0131n\u0131n en iyi oyunu buydu.Oyunun konusuna bak\u0131cak olursak gayet iyi bir hikayesi mevcut ama oyunu tam anlamak istiyosan\u0131z ilk oyundan ba\u015flaman\u0131z\u0131 tavsiye ederim oyunun hikayesini tam anlam\u0131yla anlars\u0131n\u0131z bu sefer.Grafik olarak iyi bir grafi\u011fe sahip tabi bunu g\u00fcn\u00fcm\u00fcze g\u00f6re de\u011ferlendirmemeniz laz\u0131m tekrar s\u00f6yl\u00fcyorum zaman\u0131nda ki grafi\u011fe g\u00f6re de\u011ferlendirin ve bence zaman\u0131ndaki grafi\u011fe g\u00f6re \u00e7ok iyi alman\u0131z\u0131 tavsiye ederim heleki bu tarz oyunlar\u0131 seviyor san\u0131z herkes'e iyi oyunar.\n\nHi everyone I've played almost all the games of Assassin's Creed series friends, but this time one of the best games of course there are good ones but in my opinion it was the best game of his time.If we're interested in the topic of the game there is a pretty good story, but the game I suggest you start from the first game if you want to fully understand the story of the game literally you understand this time.According to the present subject to having graphics as good as the graphics you need to evaluate it again, and I think that in time according to the time chart according to the chart, evaluate, recommend that you get the very best, especially if you have likes in this genre of games good games to everyone.", "hours": 12.1, "user_id": "76561198199750134", "username": "Winston\u2655", "products": 19, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 257, "page_order": 8, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-09-09", "text": "\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 Uplay, \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 everything it represents, \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 whoever had the idea to sell game in steam that wont be able to be played without some \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ing dumbass \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 service that no one gives a\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665about. \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 you, \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 Uplay, and \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 Ubisoft for being little \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 who sell people games just to later go: \"Well \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 me, looks like you can't play our game without signing to out great service\". \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 this, Let us play games we buy on steam in steam, if i want your \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ing Uplay i'll buy it through there, this is an offline singleplayer game, that's even more reason to not have it in some \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ing Uplay.\nedit: \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 steam censorship, stop being a little \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665.", "hours": 0.2, "username": "Maximum Beef \u30e9\u30fc\u30e1\u30f3", "products": 149, "early_access": false}
