{"product_id": "33230", "page": 259, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-09-03", "text": "One of the best games I have ever played. This is the game that got me started on the Assassin's Creed Series. Though I originally played on xbox 360; I've since started migrating my games over to steam so that my kids can't destroy the disks.\nLots of intregue, conspiracy theorists must play this game. mind blowing storyline and lots of great action.", "hours": 207.8, "username": "dcarter84", "products": 72, "early_access": false}
