{"product_id": "33230", "page": 266, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-08-04", "text": "Ezio is one of the characters I love most in videogames!\nHe had the chance to evolve in 3 different games and the story was awesome, inside and outside of the Animus.\nAfter the Ezio era, neither hero actually mattered. The story was meaningless, the protagonists weak and the \"you're the character\"+fps version of the present day is just horrible/inexistent.\nDon't get me wrong, I bought every single AC game that was released. Love them, they're fun to play. But none had the impact the 3 Ezio games had on me. Not even close... The cliffhangers at the end of each one of them were breathtaking and I miss that feeling...", "hours": 63.8, "username": "Ragnar \"Lo\u00f0br\u00f3k\" Sigurdsson", "products": 358, "early_access": false}
