{"product_id": "33230", "page": 267, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-07-27", "text": "This is a fantastic game ruined by UPlay.\nThe improvements made upon ACI are brilliant, not only has the graphics taken a bit of a leap but the gameplay additions just make this game far more memorable than the first one.\nContinuing the AC storyline Desmond finds himself in renaissance Italy. I personally find this on eth best backdrop for any of the AC games and I find that this one ahs far more gameplay involved with it also.\nI highly rate this game but only if UPlay was removed. I had to go about fixing UPlay itself as it will not work on Windows 8.1, Having to do this automatically ruins the set-up of this game. However just rating the game, I have to recommend it.", "hours": 10.2, "user_id": "76561198071705090", "username": "A Red Panda", "products": 453, "early_access": false}
