{"product_id": "33230", "page": 271, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-07-13", "text": "it's pathetic that this is still the best ac game yet\nbut that doesn't mean it's a bad game - it's \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ing amazing, one of the best open worlds i have ever played in,\na surprisingly accurate depiction of 15th century florence with an amazing story.\nbut one would think that after all these years ubisoft would have made THE ultimate AC game, but all they make is a rehashed version of ac3 with the same bugs, overly easy combat, forgettable characters, shitey pc port...\nbut they don't give a crap... seeing as they earn millions anyway... what a\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665developer.", "hours": 54.1, "user_id": "76561198039929746", "username": "Master Secretary Halfman", "products": 120, "early_access": false}
