{"product_id": "33230", "page": 278, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-06-24", "text": "This game's controls are bad. unresponsive, except when it's over sensitive, and the camera correction they built is so very unintuitive, confusing, and above all inconsistent it's embarrassing.\nThat said, it's a wicked awesome kick\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665game that has lots of content. Is fun, addictive, intriguing, challenging, nerve wracking. Like \"Thief\" & \"Batman\" rolled into one sausage calzone, eh? It doesn't have the best replay value however.\n9/10 (only because of the ridiculous \"corrective camera\")\nI've read later versions of this game have the bugs worked out of the controls so maybe try those, but this one is still unbelievably awesome.", "hours": 166.4, "user_id": "76561198170210771", "username": "thesnu", "products": 7, "early_access": false}
