{"product_id": "33230", "page": 278, "page_order": 9, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-06-22", "text": "Ezio jumped off a building I spent 10 minues scaling, jumped into the middle of a crowd I was tailing secretly, constantly messing up here and there when climbing and jumping. Races are the most horrible experience you'll ever have the misfortune of doing in your life. Having your eyes gouged out is more enjoyable than this game. great story though.\nStory 9/10\nControls -10/10\nHonestly if you're coming into the series for the first time, don't start with this game or the first...go for one that's more modern and polished...", "hours": 89.6, "username": "CHAUVICTOIRE", "products": 119, "early_access": false}
