{"product_id": "33230", "page": 279, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-06-22", "text": "Before I thought that people saying AC 2 was good, was having nostalga. As I bought and tried the game I learnt that I was wrong. This game is absolutely a masterpiece, and I would recomend it to anyone who have found interest in later (or earlier) Assassin's Creed games.\nIf you have a problem with Uplay, try to run it as administrator. I steppet on a problem where it always would crash, but if I ran it as administrator, it worked.", "hours": 45.8, "user_id": "76561198195791071", "username": "Sondstor", "products": 37, "early_access": false}
