{"product_id": "33230", "page": 286, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-06-10", "text": "Arguably the franchise's magnum opus (other contenders are Brotherhood, which is II's direct sequel, and Black Flag). Almost every single flaw from the first game are fixed on this.\nAwesome, funny, heartwarming, sad, confusing... there are all sorts of moments you will get from Assassin's Creed II.\nThe day of Uplay screw-up is long past; it's not without its flaw, of course (like updating every single time you logged in, wasting bits of time) but it's not really a reason to not recommend this.", "hours": 28.6, "username": "LazyRemnant", "products": 85, "early_access": false}
