{"product_id": "33230", "page": 292, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-05-18", "text": "It's almost the best game in the series, if not for the slightly poor performance compared to AC Revelations that's even newer than this.\nOther than that I have nothing to complain about, I like almost all the characters from Ezio, Leonardo, Claudia to, well, just about everybody... aside from Lucy, but I guess that means Lucy's story is well thought out that I already started to feel uneasy about her even before I played Brotherhood.", "hours": 22.9, "username": "JrndFrvr", "products": 194, "early_access": false}
