{"product_id": "33230", "page": 292, "page_order": 5, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-05-17", "text": "I don't know what it's like on other systems, but on a PC this game is really \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665.\nIt was difficult to get my xbox controller work with it, but eventually I debugged how to make that work.\nThen I find out that this game isn't actually sneaking up and assinating people, it's just a thinly veiled 3D running and jumping platformer with an overly complicated control system.  There's nothing fun about this \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 mess, unless you just enjoy being frustrated all day.", "hours": 1.4, "user_id": "76561198010456317", "username": "spinyfur", "products": 98, "early_access": false}
