{"product_id": "33230", "page": 303, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-03-29", "text": "The combat is fairly easy- walk behind a guy and instantly kill him with your sword.\nThe Hidden blades attack way too fast enough for the opponent to stand a chance.\nYet i think it is quite badass you can take on 10+ people with just your fists.\nI highly reccomend playing the first assassin's creed before this.\ncompleted the gamedoing just the story but i feel compelled to start this game again to do all of the little missions and 100% this game.\ni would reccomend this to 13+ ages or 10+ ad mature as there is alot of killing-if you didnt know that already. This game is kind of worth the \u00a310 but i believe it should be around \u00a35-6", "hours": 104.0, "username": "egg", "products": 29, "early_access": false}
