{"product_id": "33230", "page": 309, "page_order": 2, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-03-09", "text": "Assassin's Creed 2 requires Uplay.\nNot convinced yet? Then read on...\nUplay sucks and wouldn't save ANY progress in AC2. I wasted several hours replaying the game from the beginning since it wouldn't save any progress. I found a reliable, but stupid fix for those of you who still want to play this game:\n1. Go to:\n2. Download the save file you want.\n3. Replace your old save file with the newly downloaded save file.\n4. Launch the game and load the downloaded save file.\nI finished Assassin's Creed 2 and it's actually a really good game. It's pretty much the same as Assassin's Creed, but with some small improvements and a MUCH better story.", "hours": 21.9, "username": "ZechsX18999", "products": 221, "found_funny": 8, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 309, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-03-08", "text": "Great story, great character, This game is the CLASSIC and one of the MUST BUY things in your computer.\nThough there are a lot of bugs ( sorry ubi )  appear after updating my Mac (don't update your mac system cause then you can only see half of the picture ), I still love it.", "hours": 74.1, "user_id": "76561198156401018", "username": "NORAtheJELLYFISH", "products": 75, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 309, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-03-08", "text": "Great game! Would have been awesome if no internet connection was required. The game was great, the story was fun, side quests were also fun, great character and assassin robe. Only negative thing to this game for me is the internet connection. I run on slow internet and it was constantly losing connection during the middle of missions forcing me to wait until my internet started working again. This caused me to get through the story quickly because it was really annoying. Looking at this game would have been amazing if my internet was good.", "hours": 27.5, "user_id": "76561198108743170", "username": "CaptainSnugly", "products": 65, "early_access": false}
