{"product_id": "33230", "page": 310, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-03-01", "text": "This is still one of my favorite games. Everything works great together, the story, the parkour, the combat and graphics. I 100% ed the PS3 version and when this came up on deep discount, I bought it again with no regrets. Great entry point to the series, the original can be skipped entirely with nothing lost.", "hours": 47.1, "user_id": "76561198070516394", "username": "BLove", "products": 770, "early_access": false}
