{"product_id": "33230", "page": 326, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-01-10", "text": "Assassins Creed 2 puts you into the shoes of Ezio Auditore, an ambitious and charismatic character that feels very much alive. The story and flow of the game works perfectly and gets better and better, the beginning being one of my favorite intros in games. Although on the other hand the ending seemed really\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 the story could have ended in so many better ways, yet we are given with a big surprise and the biggest mind\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 in history. Although much respect for the game we are also complimented by beautiful music, that fits carefully with the game. The world is huge and massive and the game takes quite long to finish, around a 20 hour storyline (purely main quests). Overall the game starts brilliantly, and progresses on, and ends \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ily. 9/10", "hours": 14.2, "user_id": "76561198046449299", "username": "Das Reich\u2122", "products": 44, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 326, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-01-09", "text": "Updated:\nIt finally works. I had to folow the steps exposed in the following link nevertheless:\nStill fed up with the whole \"uplay\" thing. I Find it useless to players and time consuming. In the other hand I find out the game matches my expectations now that it works properly. I like specially the graphical tinkerings allowed. I play in a laptop and need to downgrade the quality in order to get it works it properly.\nSo leaving aside the whole annoying Uplay thing, I think I have to recommend the game. It's a good job.\nFinalmente funciona si se siguen los pasos del siguiente enlace:\nSigo molesto con el tema del Uplay, que considero una molestia y una p\u00e9rdida de tiempo, pero el juego est\u00e1 a la altura, ahora que funciona. Dejando a un lado el problema del Uplay, considero que merece la pena. Es un buen juego.\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------\nOld comment\nThe stupid Uplay thing, wich you have to conect previous to play no matter if you want or not, launches an error message after longing in, so I can\u00b4t begin to play. The game doesn\u00b4t run. I\u00b4m fed up with all those idiot DRM systems wich only gets troubles and time wasting. This is their only use; to get your time wasted once and again. I\u00b4m really fed up. Hate those things and I can\u00b4t play my game. Congratulations ubisoft; another customer unsatisfied.\nHarto ya de los DRM y todas esas tonter\u00edas que requieren registrarse antes de jugar. S\u00f3lo te aportan una p\u00e9rdida de tiempo constante y molestias. Estoy muy harto. En este caso, adem\u00e1s el juego no arranca. El Uplay de las narices lanza un mensaje de error y no permite iniciarlo, as\u00ed que enhorabuena, Ubisoft. Otro cliente insatisfecho.", "hours": 5.0, "user_id": "76561198044663578", "username": "moonlightdrop", "products": 266, "early_access": false}
