{"product_id": "33230", "page": 333, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-01-01", "text": "Okay - I changed my Review from Bad to Good - That I could not start the Game in the first Place and I had to look for solutions for more then 4 Hours is still bad, but it was a Driver related Story. The Game stopped loading after it passed the UBI Launcher - so it was a long time my Main Target. But then I paied more attention to my Sounddriver. I deinstalled and installed the Sounddriver and right after that the Game started properly and runs stable and great now - happy New Year :-)", "hours": 2.4, "username": "[US]Laird Comanche[D]", "products": 141, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 333, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-01-01", "text": "One of the best assassin's creed In the series but the controls are a little different from the assassin's creed now since they have easier controls and better graphics so if you like story based assassins creed i would get it but if your more just kill everything then i wouldnt and dont let the uplay reviews get to you i havent had a single problem with uplay.", "hours": 17.9, "user_id": "76561198153586290", "username": "Spartan112", "products": 85, "early_access": false}
