{"product_id": "33230", "page": 346, "page_order": 2, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-12-19", "text": "The game's itself is a masterpiece. However Uplay ruins it. I had many problems installing the game and now steam doesn't detect whether I'm in game or not. I can't shift + tab to open steam. And many other problems. Why, because Ubisoft is smart. I'm buying games from steam because i want to play them from steam, not another silly app. I recommend this game and voted NO only because of Uplay.", "hours": 24.7, "user_id": "76561198038359171", "username": "GriHaci", "products": 40, "early_access": false}
