{"product_id": "33230", "page": 346, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-12-19", "text": "Being the second Assassin's Creed game, starting the trilogy of well known Ezio Auditore da Firenze. A young assassin getting revenge and becoming the leader. This game has the longest and most complex story, which if you like - you are going to enjoy the game a lot more. It has lot actions to offer, many main and side missions, random public events, etc. Controls staying almost the same as in first Assassin's Creed. 'Vittoria agli Assassini.'", "hours": 47.2, "username": "Silencer", "products": 161, "early_access": false}
