{"product_id": "33230", "page": 348, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-12-14", "text": "This is my first Assassin's Creed series game.Just take a look at the time I spent playing it,  I would like to recommand it to everyone who has interest in the assassin-based theme game.\nThe brilliant attacking movement and the fantastic assassin art showed by the character you control along with the cohesive plots together make great contribution to its success. Besides this, while you are experencing the famous assassin Ezio auditore' s life, you will learn the history of the auditore family and realize everthing in the game  happens for a reason. BTW, the renaissance style architecture and the beautiful countryside views make you feel relaxed between exciting assassinations.\nYou won't regret having it and hope you all have great fun in this game.", "hours": 105.9, "user_id": "76561198049545660", "username": "FREESCALE", "products": 7, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 348, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-12-13", "text": "The game itself is a substantial upgrade from the first Assassin's Creed, pretty much everything from the first game has been redone and polished to perfection. Everything from scenery, weapons, enemy AI, proper placement and design of buildings for climbing, level progression, difficulty curve has been implemented magnificently.\nGraphics are very pretty especially the scenery during the daytime, however sometimes the faces on people look...laminated.\nVariance on assassinations have expanded greatly in this game, you can pick and choose how you want to execute your kill. Everything from knives, swords, hidden blade, guns or just using plain fists.\nA masterpiece of a game, it's like they actually listened to all the suggestions and criticism aimed at the first game and made Assassin's Creed II.", "hours": 26.3, "user_id": "76561197977450814", "username": "HyperDebtRay", "products": 276, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 348, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-12-13", "text": "20 Years without food and still surviving 20/10", "hours": 37.4, "username": "VACBANNED PERMANENT DISACTIVE", "products": 7, "found_funny": 2, "early_access": false}
