{"product_id": "33230", "page": 348, "page_order": 5, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-12-13", "text": "I very rarely write reviews. I was unable to ge this game working after spending 2-3 hours online trying to fix Uplay. I have uninstalled it and will refrain from buying Ubisoft games with Uplay in the future. I own quite a few games and this is the first one ever that I was not able to get working.", "hours": 0.3, "user_id": "76561197972051839", "username": "Malbec", "products": 208, "early_access": false}
