{"product_id": "33230", "page": 350, "page_order": 0, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-12-09", "text": "Kind of a hit and miss game. Some bits work, others don't which can leave you feeling very frustrated. Since this is the only Assassin's Creed game I've played, I can't compare it to the rest, but it's quite hard to recommend unless you're really into this sort of game.", "hours": 5.7, "user_id": "76561198007231821", "username": "Jacobite", "products": 174, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 350, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-12-08", "text": "In my personal opinion this is the better Assassin's Creed Game, it has a good plot, great gameplay, graphics are good for the year of release, exept for the horrible draw distance, a lot of side quests and character improvements, (armors, weapons , art and s.h.i.t for your villa, that produces more money if you invest in it, etc.) well ...very good game buy it.", "hours": 25.9, "username": "cako82", "products": 105, "early_access": false}
