{"product_id": "33230", "page": 352, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-12-05", "text": "An extremely fun open world sandbox adventure game.\nThe story isn't exactly oscar worthy but the game is much less repetitive than AC1.\nItaly looks and feels amazing. Definitely recommend!", "hours": 36.3, "username": "Yergnoe", "products": 381, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 352, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-12-04", "text": "Wow,I am so upset with myself I did not play this game when it came out,The game is awesome and its SO LONG,with campaign 21 hours & 10+ misc. that game has to offer,there is more to this game,History about Italy in the the past (15th century) and the smooth gameplay. I like this game,give it a try ;)\n8/10", "hours": 19.9, "username": "fuzzybuzzy", "products": 115, "early_access": false}
