{"product_id": "33230", "page": 353, "page_order": 5, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-12-02", "text": "I really want to like this game, but this is probably the worst form imaginable to play it in. First of all, this game desperately requires a controller, but the mac version does not support one. It barely even supports my keyboard. The controlls are incredibly clunky. I have literaly spent 90% of my time on this game trying to get it to work. Not to mention the fact that it requires UPlay, one of the greatest sins humanity has ever commited. This is a good game, but it is the worst port to pc I've ever seen.", "hours": 10.7, "username": "thekarreg", "products": 204, "early_access": false}
