{"product_id": "33230", "page": 355, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-11-30", "text": "I've spent some time to finish this game, it is AWESOME!\nTravel over Italy and Vatican to spready Justice and an atmosphere of Vengeance.\nEzio Auditore is one of the best character on all of the franchise.\nAttack animation, Death animation, kill animation is all great.\nThis game when the old Ubisoft knows how to create a good missions.\n\"Leonardo, i've bring some more pages\" \"Ah! Ezio how exciting!\"\nRIDING CARRIAGE CROSS OVER THE ALPHINE MOUNTAINS, FLYING WITH A PAPER BAT ACROSS VENICE,\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ON A GONDOLA/BOAT. IT'S ALL IN, ONLY IN ASSASSINS CREED 2.\nI know i sounds like an advertiser but no \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 YOU ALL. TY 9.99/11. (wait what)\nDefinitely an awesome game if you want to throwback to the golden age of gaming! ahah", "hours": 19.0, "username": "Jakerat Autism", "products": 38, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 355, "page_order": 4, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-11-30", "text": "This is the first review I have ever written, and with a heavy heart I cannot recomend this game. At the very start of the game, (right after the intro) the entire screen goes white, but the game still functions, (menu, sound, ect...) I tried re-downloading the game, restarting my computer, and e-maling both steam and uplay. I will change my review as soon as this problem is adressed because I love the Assassin's creed series.", "hours": 0.9, "user_id": "76561198116134607", "username": "brandonfast34", "products": 46, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 355, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-11-30", "text": "If your here and loved the first Assassin's Creed well this will not disappoint.\nSame stealth mechanic, using different weapons and wear a \"bad-@ss\" hood.\nPace through the game as you get to explore, best you foes with smooth combat and new weapons as well as more cool parkour.\nWhat's New?:\n-Explore some cities in 15th century Italy\n-Upgradable Armour (optional Alta\u00efr costume)\n-Buy and choose different weapons\n-the coolest thing ever the double assassination\nA great game with another original story and same unique game mechanics for the first AC, another i would love to play again.", "hours": 73.0, "username": "Mr_Non_Member", "products": 92, "early_access": false}
