{"product_id": "33230", "page": 357, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-11-27", "text": "BEST ASSASSIN'S CREED GAME EVER!\nI've played from Assassin's Creed I to Assassin's Creed IV: Black Flag and this one is still my favorite, Not only the story is long enough and very interesting, but the gameplay is different and fun, and my dear Ezio Auditore da Firenze (I also consider him the best assassin ever) is a very charismatic person, he's funny, he's good with the ladies, and of course, he's handsome as hell, if you ever doubt if you should buy this game or not, don't doubt it, BUY IT NOW! It's worth every cent c:", "hours": 49.7, "username": "Kaybi", "products": 289, "early_access": false}
