{"product_id": "33230", "page": 359, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-11-23", "text": "This is my first Assassin's Creed game in the franchise.  after playing 44.5 hours and still not quite through, I finally realized the hype over Assassin's Creed.\nThe history learned of each city, historical figures and gameplay itself is amazing.\nBeautiful graphics, rich story, and loads of game play time.", "hours": 150.0, "username": "drgn_assassin4", "products": 45, "early_access": false}
