{"product_id": "33230", "page": 359, "page_order": 6, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-11-22", "text": "Most cause of death: automatic camera rotation, and they don't just rotate to mess us your direction of WSAD, they \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ing lock them that way. The camera angels for climbing puzzle are extraordinarily retard, they were so painful that it is near impossible to survive due to the time window. It happens way too \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ing often when you press W to move forward your character moves in different direction and jumps right off a cliff and dies.\n\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 YOU CAMERA", "hours": 35.3, "username": "IZftw", "products": 262, "early_access": false}
