{"product_id": "33230", "page": 361, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-11-17", "text": "First time playing any AC game, read the tutorial.\n\"Press the green foot button on your keyboard to sprint\"\n10/10 no flaws at all", "hours": 1.4, "username": "[GC]Henkedew", "products": 158, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 361, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-11-17", "text": "Many people consider this the height of the series, as did I for a very long time. I think Black Flag really encapsulates the best AC has to offer but that doesn't mean I don't respect the hell out of AC2. I never really did quite love Ezio the same way other people did but he's an alright character and I appreciate that they take the time to develop him throughout his apperances in the franchise.\nBut, definitely play this game. There's a wonkyness in the controls which can be kind of rough sometimes but its a huge game, thats for sure, with a long story and lots to explore and get stuck in.", "hours": 40.4, "username": "Slowbro", "products": 469, "early_access": false}
