{"product_id": "33230", "page": 362, "page_order": 8, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-11-15", "text": "Hate if need to register and login somwhere else afer launching game in steam. Trying to register as a new user and got answer that username (my email) is already associated with uplay account. Ok. So I'm forgotten the password and recover the password could be a good choice. But so far no recoveri mails found.. And so is gone 1 hour playing time already.. Muahhahahaa :D\nSteam storepage should have info about needed extra accounts and staff like this to avoid this kind of 'fun'.\nDon't know anything about game yet.", "hours": 15.2, "user_id": "76561197985462570", "username": "___Funny___", "products": 62, "early_access": false}
