{"product_id": "33230", "page": 364, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-11-13", "text": "Another Xbox 360 repurchase.\nThis is still the best Assassin's Creed game, particularly because it is the least glitchy and the progression is the most rewarding. Ezio is also still the best written character in the series.\nI find this runs better than on consoles in general. Apart from one glitch I never encountered before.\nI like the time period. I like the weapons, the art, the culture, the history.\nThis marked THE high point in everything Ubisoft, in my opinion.", "hours": 21.8, "username": "Quillion", "products": 167, "early_access": false}
