{"product_id": "33230", "page": 381, "page_order": 1, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-10-09", "text": "UNPLAYABLE!\nDO NOT BUY THIS GAME IF YOU'RE ON A MAC!\nThey really messed up the controls, the keyboard doesn't respond (the game thinks the MOUSE is the keyboard) so the only way to move is to disconnect the mouse when you start the game and reconnect it again when the game has started.\nThe mouse input is terrible, there is NO control over sensitivity or anything and stutters a lot and there is no way to get rid of it.\nAgain: NO NOT BUY THIS GAME, at least not if you're on a Mac!!\nIt's a rip-off, very disappointing and truely sad that such an old game isn't properly ported and yet still sold.\nEven for 2.5\u20ac it feels like a waste of money.", "hours": 0.4, "user_id": "76561197962281599", "username": "GeneralPain", "products": 34, "early_access": false}
