{"product_id": "33230", "page": 381, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-10-09", "text": "Assassins Creed II is an amazing game. The story is great. You play Ezio Auditore da Firenze (Ezio Auditore of Florence) who [Spoiler Alert] witnesses the death of his father and brothers, which leads him to a huge Italian journey wrapped in revenge.", "hours": 10.2, "user_id": "76561198065648228", "username": "Your Resident Metalhead Rishal", "products": 108, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 381, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-10-09", "text": "The game that almost replaced HL2 in my heart, but not quite.\nBrilliant piece of stroytelling, deep and intriguing, wonderful music, gorgeous immersive graphics and atmospheres, and genuinely believable characters.  Ezio, Machiavelli, legendary stuff.\nI love the historical accurace Ubisoft carry in all of their games, job well done!", "hours": 56.7, "user_id": "76561198012689396", "username": "Detective Joost Van Der Kracht", "products": 101, "early_access": false}
