{"product_id": "33230", "page": 390, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-09-12", "text": "Very fun game. My first and favourite in the series by far. Not a perfect game, i.e, repetetive animations, glitchy as f*ck, mildly \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 ai. However, if you are a fan of the series you can get past all that. Good story, many hours of side missions and collectible hunting. Great game. 4/5", "hours": 32.0, "user_id": "76561198119654885", "username": "TheDankDinosaur", "products": 140, "early_access": false}
