{"product_id": "33230", "page": 392, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-08-29", "text": "I love the beautiful graphics and dynamic story of this game. Everything is very smooth and life-like, and the quality is constant throughout the game (interactive and video). I think it's great there's is an option to turn off the blood splatters, which even carries over to the story video sequences, and there is minimal (some, though infrequent) foul language. As an open world, you can explore all you want and get back to the story (major or minor) when you feel like it. I've been looking for a game with this much quality effort put into it for a long time, and am quite satisfied so far. It's no wonder this series is such a success! This is the first Assassin's Creed game I have played, and I am very happy with my choice. Five stars!", "hours": 86.9, "user_id": "76561198151162951", "username": "goatvet.sb", "products": 17, "early_access": false}
