{"product_id": "33230", "page": 395, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-08-15", "text": "One of the best Assassins Creed titles ever!\nThe story is rich and detailed and the action is fluid and exciting\nTravel across Renaissance Italy, taking down those involved in your family's betrayal\nWield your dual blades, a sword or any other weapon with ease and takedown those who oppose you\nWhat Assassins Creed 1 provided, AC2 improves immensely\nIf you must try an Assassins Creed game, take this one for a spin\nI did, and have been hooked ever since", "hours": 228.0, "user_id": "76561198008751254", "username": "Robert", "products": 175, "early_access": false}
