{"product_id": "33230", "page": 404, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-07-11", "text": "I love this game so much!!!\nAnother successful game from Ubisoft that showed the sequel of the original and genius story in a fictional-historical setting of renaissance Italy with all the other new features since the first Assassin's Creed, for example: the ability to buy weapons and armor instead of earning it through gameplay.\ni don't think or seen any cons on this game cause' it's awesome.", "hours": 55.6, "username": "Mandellla", "products": 738, "early_access": false}
