{"product_id": "33230", "page": 406, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-07-06", "text": "As I work my way through the series, I must say this is leaps and bounds better than the first game. The same three missions are gone, and now a seemless story with believable missions. I found myself sitting there for hours lost inside this game. I highly recommed this game way more than the first, as this seems to be where the real story begins.", "hours": 32.4, "username": "dzinction", "products": 360, "early_access": false}
