{"product_id": "33230", "page": 409, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-07-02", "text": "Pretty fantastic game and a huge improvement on 1.  Instead of a blank slate grr-grr character, you play Ezio, who is pretty well defined.  Story is more relevant, though not by a lot (revenge instead of whatever the \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 was going on in 1).  Guards are less annoying than in 1, and, well, just... everything is so much better.  This game is great and you should play it if you haven't already.\n...Though, how old is it now?", "hours": 21.2, "user_id": "76561197985881367", "username": "Lucius Brimstone", "products": 491, "early_access": false}
