{"product_id": "33230", "page": 413, "page_order": 4, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-06-28", "text": "Please don't buy this game.\nI mean its ok I guess, but the graphics are outdated. I'm sure they looked cool and realistic at the time, but now they're just creepy. The controls aren't clear for people playing without a plug in controller. The worst thing though is stupid Uplay, which is ubisofts way of forcing you to make an account on a website which would've looked bad in 1990.\nIt's a good enough game, the story's ok or whatever, but it's outdated, and you'd be better just buying a newer assassins creed.", "hours": 2.2, "user_id": "76561198096126039", "username": "square bubbles", "products": 24, "early_access": false}
