{"product_id": "33230", "page": 417, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-06-24", "text": "Personally the AC series is probably one of my top favorite game series. I have played every AC game and thoroughly enjoyed every one of them. However AC 2 is the best one so far because of it's fantastic story, it's revolutionary features that changed the series, and it's just plain fun. Period. I would highly recommend this game as well as all the other AC games. If you enjoy them then I'm happy to know that AC got more fans. If you didn't that's alright, it's just not for you which is fine.", "hours": 1.3, "user_id": "76561198030978104", "username": "Tylermcd93", "products": 247, "early_access": false}
