{"product_id": "33230", "page": 420, "page_order": 4, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-06-21", "text": "I couldn't even get this game to work, let alone review the content. After going through the pains of setting up a Uplay account and linking it to the game, having it crash every single time I loaded it, I finally got it to open. It froze, wouldn't recognize my mouse, and made it impossible to select anything from a menu by having the selector constantly move downward. And it still sometimes crashes when I try to open it. I don't know how it works on Windows (I am running OS X Mavericks), but I would not recommend this game to any Mac user.", "hours": 30.9, "user_id": "76561198128392939", "username": "Mad Vlad", "products": 206, "early_access": false}
