{"product_id": "33230", "page": 423, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-06-15", "text": "Truly, the height of the series and the inspiration for a deeper and amazing saga of games.\nOverall - 9.2/10, highly recommended~\nVisuals & Story - 9/10\nEven by modern standards, AC2 delivers a stylized and immersive experience with rich, detailed environments.\nI combined story and visual style for the ability of a game to deliver that in it's own organic way, to which AC2 performs beautifully.\n-1 for a few repeatative structures and minor \"open world\" claustrophobia.\nAudo & Music - 10/10\nI played the game entirely in Italian w/ Eng subs and it was enthralling.  The music is perfect.\nGameplay - 8/10\nFor all the fun and features, ease of control and intuitive free-running, epic puzzles and quests...\n-1 for the enemies being rather repeatative\n-1 for no epic bosses", "hours": 41.2, "user_id": "76561198040684302", "username": "\u06af\u03c1\u044f\u0457\u05e4\u05e4\u0105\u014b: :\u039e\u04b2\u00cd\u0141\u04d8", "products": 136, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 423, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-06-14", "text": "40 hrs of solid game play with a little sidequests here and there, great plot, graphics still look great for the current day and age and for this price its a steal. All I can say what re you waiting for!!!", "hours": 38.7, "user_id": "76561198116106491", "username": "Blitz", "products": 225, "early_access": false}
