{"product_id": "33230", "page": 424, "page_order": 7, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-06-07", "text": "I can't get this game past the login popup because of the faulty Ubisoft Launcher (at least, that's what 5 other people having the same issue with the same damn game have concluded, another 20 people blame Uplay). Ubisoft is mostly to blame for this I'm sure (they're sort of notorious for being less user friendly than the Xbox 1 in it's 24/7 spying days), but I still wouldn't recommend paying 20$ for this game if you wouldn't be able to fix that on your own. I'm incredibly disappointed about all this because 1 I spent 20$ f--king dollars on a game that won't work because it has a busted launcher inside of a game that is SUPPOSED to have it's OWN F--KING LAUNCHER, and because the music and gameplay I've seen look beautiful...", "hours": 185.6, "username": "Secundox", "products": 50, "early_access": false}
