{"product_id": "33230", "page": 437, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-03-24", "text": "In my humble opinion I have to agree, that this Assassin's Creed version is by far the best part of the Assassin's Creed tetralogy.\nYes, the graphics got a lot better in the following parts III and IV; but you have to admit, that the ambience and atmosphere is what the Assassin's Creed games should also be well provided,\ne.g. follwing the Credo of the Assassin's brotherhood and acting like a true Assassin is just at the  peak in this second part of the tetralogy.\nPlus the story AND the gameplay will make you satisfied, if you love the genre.", "hours": 30.8, "username": "WUF3RUS", "products": 38, "early_access": false}
