{"product_id": "33230", "page": 448, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-22", "text": "A must-have for any Assassin's Creed fan. If you liked AC3, this will definitely impress you. This game is much like Arkham Asylum. Beautiful visuals, groovy music, and very detailed controls. If you like to climb city corners and perform kill moves on the job, this is your game.", "hours": 14.7, "username": "HatefulPreacher", "products": 193, "early_access": false}
