{"product_id": "33230", "page": 449, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-17", "text": "+Best storyline in all of Assassin's Creed games and one of the best I have ever seen. Great plot twists and characters as well.\n+Likeable protagonist who changes as time passes\n+Adds many new features and improvements to the series while remaining loyal to its predecessor.\n+Really long (I played through this on UPlay which is why Steam shows  so little playtime.)\n+Great dialogue\n+The music and sounds fit really well\n+Excellent soundtrack\n+Huge world with lots of things to do in it\n+Rewarding collectibles\n+Each assassination allows you to do it your way\n+Historically accurate\n-The controls have small problems with them\n-Slightly too easy\n10/10, deserved its GOTY", "hours": 2.4, "username": "BajES", "products": 171, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 450, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-16", "text": "it's \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ing assassin's creed why wouldn't i recommend this!", "hours": 19.5, "user_id": "76561198070080409", "username": "Supertuesday", "products": 13, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 450, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-16", "text": "Assassin's Creed 2 is a great sequel from where AC1 started it off. It's true the original can be considered a prototype of an original idea with many things doing wrong, I played the director\u2019s cut, it's still lacking... Even though there is a fast-travel system in place...\nPeople will enjoy AC2 a lot, though it is true that many will find lacking in challenge. The soundtrack is great, though going back on AC1 you\u2019d agree that shouldn\u2019t really be a surprise.\nCombat is yet again quite poor, the economy of the 15th century Italian states seems to be in flux as well (people call it Renaissance era, but in all honesty it\u2019s the late middle ages).\nBtw: Ubisoft started its \u201cUplay\u201d system with this game, good or bad, we have it now\u2026", "hours": 103.6, "user_id": "76561198073927253", "username": "von Sanneck", "products": 174, "early_access": false}
