{"product_id": "33230", "page": 457, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-01-13", "text": "Definitely a great story. Hands down, AC2 is worth $20.  It was originally designed for consoles, so the keyboard+mouse can be tricky.  If you're afraid of heights, this game might trip your bawls off. Whatever...just buy this\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665", "hours": 34.4, "username": "ineffable", "products": 198, "early_access": false}
