{"product_id": "33230", "page": 457, "page_order": 6, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-01-13", "text": "Assassin's Creed 2 is an adventurous action game about a young boy named Ezio Auditore De Firenze where you have to use certain actions that seeks revenge on Templars for getting their loved ones hanged. The game is full of action-packed action actions and actions.", "hours": 51.8, "username": "m1t^", "products": 67, "early_access": false}
