{"product_id": "33230", "page": 460, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-01-03", "text": "the mac port is kind of a mess - random hang-ups (when typical FPS is 20s-30s) and a crash-causing glitch that occurs every time I happen to be pressing the high-profile, directional, legs and focus buttons. the game is by no means unplayable, and these problems are almost definitely not going to get fixed, but they're still frustrating.", "hours": 43.6, "username": "kazooiedog", "products": 31, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 460, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-01-03", "text": "BUY BUY BUY , this game its just everything a gamer could ever wwant in a game. and probably the one of the best Assassin creed's Games made! graphics 10/10,  story 10/10 , plus you can run around and assasinate people, who wouldnt wanna do that. the game encorperates a huge free world map that you can explore if you please,  your character can also climb the highest of buildings with no problem at all. parhour everysingle part of them game 10/10 game buy it !", "hours": 37.3, "username": "Sassy", "products": 75, "early_access": false}
