{"product_id": "33230", "page": 460, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-01-03", "text": "This is probably the best Assassin's Creed game i have played.\nThis game has an amazing storyline, great graphics and animation for its age and i really love the soundtracks!\nIf you're an Assassin's Creed fan, you know that Ezio is the easiest assassin to relate to and get attached to.\nIf you're going to play this game on PC i highly recommend using a XinPut controller or use an emulator for a DS3 controller. PS4 controller works great on it, but using a keyboard and mouse on Assassin's Creed is going to hurt your experience...", "hours": 33.8, "username": "Maxtez [FO]", "products": 139, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 460, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-01-03", "text": "This game is alot of fun. It captures the feel of 16th and 17th century italy in a very immersive way. The stealth and combat are solidly designed but a little oo easy if anything. ezio is a charismatic and entertaining character. this is one of my favourite games and by far the best assassins creed game. It does however suffer from poor instructions on the controls and is a little too easy but these are minor subtractions 8.8/10", "hours": 323.7, "username": "ENFIELD", "products": 152, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
