{"product_id": "33230", "page": 461, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-01-02", "text": "This game may very well be my favorite game to come out of the seventh generation of gaming. Seriously, Assassin's Creed II fixes everything that was wrong with it's predecessor. It has a very fluid (albeit slightly complex) control and fighting system, it has good variation in gameplay, and the story is pretty good overall. If you haven't played this game yet, I do highly recommend it.", "hours": 26.8, "username": "Gooshi | mgf~", "products": 293, "early_access": false}
