{"product_id": "33230", "page": 463, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-12-30", "text": "Game: Assassin's Creed II Deluxe Edition\nGenre: Action/Stealth\nDeveloper: Ubisoft\nSystem: Steam (PC)\nTotal Score: 90/100\nValue Score: 9.0/10\n\u2022 Story: 10/10\n\u2022 Characters: 10/10\n\u2022 GamePlay: 10/10\n\u2022 Graphics: 9/10\n\u2022 Sound: 10/10\n\u2022 Music: 7/10\n\u2022 Length: 8/10\n\u2022 Replay Value: 6/10\n\u2022 Player Value: 10/10\nPros\n+Improved gameplay mechanics with a lot of great new additions\n+Improved storyline elements and puzzle elements\n+A longer campaign/story mode\n+Better protagonist and colorful cast of characters compared to the original\n+Improved visuals and overall design\nCons\n-Still the usual bug here and there involving NPCs\n-Music is still forgettable at times\n-Absolutely no replay value compared to the original", "hours": 35.4, "username": "Basilicious", "products": 1411, "early_access": false}
