{"product_id": "33230", "page": 472, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-12-16", "text": "Phewwwww Just took a trip through Italy in the great Renaissance Times..... and it was fun! This game is a must play one of the best in the year and really took a turn in graphics. It had an amazing story following the first game with a new character named Etzio (I think i spelled that right). Still Desmond must fight in the present time to defeat the templars and go in \"baby\" to see his ancestors past secrets. Great game I wish I didn't waste as many time on the side missions, but hey i completed it and it was good. I would say all is good except one problem I hope they do fix is when you climb buildings and such that you kind of have a tendenacy to jump off when pressing the A buton. Ah well :D I hope you all play it too whoever reads this.", "hours": 64.6, "username": "Moon", "products": 1234, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 472, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-12-15", "text": "The best Assassin's Creed game. No AC game since has really captured the magic of this game.", "hours": 37.8, "username": "Lucoque", "products": 276, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 472, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-12-15", "text": "A major improvement on the first game, this game is the basis of what makes an Assassin's Creed game.\nIf you're used to the newer combat system from AC3 and 4, or if you're used to the faster paced combat of Brotherhood and Revelations, combat might seem a bit slow in 2, but it's definitely not a huge annoyance.\nA word of warning for people who would buy it for mac: there are unresolved issues (no keyboard response, is just one) with the mac version, and there's no reason to think these issues will ever be fixed. If you can bootcamp, I definitely recommend to do that, as the game will both RUN better on the SAME hardware AND there will be no issues.", "hours": 136.7, "username": "Olivier", "products": 339, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 473, "page_order": 0, "recommended": false, "date": "2013-12-14", "text": "Can i refund this ?\nthe game is fine and its fun to play\nit has a good story but the QTE for pc are terrible >.>\nand ontop of that when sprinting on roofs its almost impossible to navigate accuratly 100% of the time\nthis game is clearly made for console the only ups i can give this is how good it looks / runs on pc\noh and there is the huge issue of not being able to play offline or alt tab if your running on a mac...\nye this litrally makes it impossible for me the play the game a lot of the time .... this is a wast of money for me", "hours": 4.8, "user_id": "76561198003900231", "username": "Syther", "products": 181, "early_access": false}
