{"product_id": "33230", "page": 478, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-11-28", "text": "Awesome Story, Gameplay and Ezio is just pure awesome!!! The city is so huge that I want to explore the whole City. Killing innocent civillians is just hillarious. Fighting system is excellent! The combat finishing moves are just pure BADASS!!!!\nOverall a wonderful game!!!! I give it a 9/10", "hours": 42.6, "username": "CayCayInCave", "products": 13, "early_access": false}
