{"product_id": "33230", "page": 478, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-11-27", "text": "This was my first introduction into the Assassin's Series and it would be an excellent beginning point thanks to the ease of gameplay and the excellent story. It begins Ezio's line of story and is very engrossing and the free-roaming mechanicals are fantastic. I still thoroughly enjoy playing this game, and the series revolutionized the sandbox genre by paving the way for compelling story AND gameplay.", "hours": 70.4, "user_id": "76561198018559999", "username": "ArkateraZ25", "products": 199, "early_access": false}
