{"product_id": "33230", "page": 479, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-11-27", "text": "Even if you didn't like AC1 (I found it repetitive both gameplay and location-wise) this resets the entire experience. Lovable characters, amazing gameplay, brilliant settings, fun story. One of my favorite games of all time.", "hours": 75.9, "username": "Resplendent", "products": 285, "early_access": false}
