{"product_id": "33230", "page": 479, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-11-27", "text": "Really good game, in my opinion the best in the series. Gameplay is fast, graphics are nice and Ezio's story is awesome. I finished the main storyline in about 13 hours. The rest was just playing around or doing secondary missions. I recommend it to anyone interested this type of games.", "hours": 28.5, "username": "Moddingspree", "products": 199, "early_access": false}
