{"product_id": "33230", "page": 482, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-11-15", "text": "Einfach nur geiles Spiel top Story und Alles. Einzigstes Problem: Man sollte Waffen zum Abfeuern z.b. Pistolen und Wurfmesser mit einem Art Fadenkreuz machen. Ansonst nur zu empfehlen.", "hours": 28.1, "user_id": "76561198087414260", "username": "nk6336", "products": 26, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 482, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-11-14", "text": "When it runs smoothly and doesn't shove story missions in your face it's excellent fun. Large numbers of enemies to fight and areas to explore. Engaging and challenging, without drowning you in objectives or equipment as later games in the series do.\nClear improvement over the first game, although the new main character takes some getting used to.\nHowever, at other times it'll demand you complete some boring story mission or worse flying mission, filled with annoying pre-requisites and arbitrary \"stealth\" sections, which have insta-fail conditions.\nTakes a bit of hardware to run smoothly - the freerunning will have you tearing your hair out if it lags.", "hours": 38.5, "user_id": "76561198010975202", "username": "Hunty820", "products": 63, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 482, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-11-13", "text": "Tak tahle hra m\u011b chytla a u\u017e nepustila. V\u00fdborn\u00e1 historick\u00e1 ak\u010dn\u00ed v\u00fdprava se skv\u011bl\u00fdm p\u0159\u00edb\u011bhem, grafikou i hratelnost\u00ed. Atmosf\u00e9ra v\u00e1s zcela pohlt\u00ed a tak tu m\u00e1me vynikaj\u00edc\u00ed ak\u010dn\u00ed adventuru v otev\u0159en\u00e9m sv\u011bt\u011b, kter\u00e1 zaru\u010d\u00ed hodiny z\u00e1bavy. Stereotyp je u podobn\u00fdch her vedlej\u0161\u00edmi \u00fa\u010dinky, ov\u0161em r\u00e1di ho zde p\u0159ekousnete.Boj\u00edm, \u017ee tohle u\u017e kluci z Ubisoftu nep\u0159ekonaj\u00ed. No, uvid\u00edme, ale tady je to jasn\u011b zaslou\u017een\u00fdch 10/10.  Grazie, Ezio. Riposi in pace.\nPS: Jenom doporu\u010duji hr\u00e1t na ovlada\u010di.", "hours": 24.3, "username": "EaZy", "products": 107, "early_access": false}
