{"product_id": "33230", "page": 482, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-11-05", "text": "Assassin's Creed 2 is an epic story of family, vengeance and conspiracy set in the pristine, yet brutal, backdrop of a Renaissance Italy. Ezio befriends Leonardo da Vinci, takes on Florence's most powerful families and ventures throughout the canals of Venice where he learns to become a master assassin. Epic Story and beautiful design.", "hours": 24.8, "username": "Grand Master Gore", "products": 511, "early_access": false}
