{"product_id": "33230", "page": 483, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-10-25", "text": "10/10 the best game out of the assassins creed series. The story line to this game is amazing and it can get a little repetitive but stilll one of my favorite games I have ever played. Go buy the game right now", "hours": 0.8, "username": "red_head55", "products": 169, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 483, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-10-25", "text": "Amazing. A must to get.\nedited 10/12/16\nA marvelous game with a great story. The PC port however is trash. There's a ridiculously bad shadow pop in distance, and on certain higher end cards the game stutters like hell. It's a nice game, but only buy it on steam if you want to ignore the issues that are in this version.", "hours": 164.5, "username": "pipe", "products": 103, "early_access": false}
