{"product_id": "33230", "page": 484, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-10-05", "text": "PL:  Zdecydowanie najlepsza cz\u0119\u015b\u0107 serii, kreatywno\u015b\u0107 w szczytowej formie zanim Ubi poczu\u0142o \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 dochod\u00f3w z corocznych cz\u0119\u015bci. Oferowane atrakcje to\n. niecodzienne t\u0142o historyczne, kilka pi\u0119knych miast do zwiedzenia, bohater o bogatej osobowo\u015bci i muzyka Jaspera Kyda  (weterana serii Hitman).\nENG:  The best installment in the series by far, the peak of creativity before Ubi tasted the profits from annual installments. Among other things, it offers: an unusual setting, a few picturesque towns to explore, a protagonist rich in character, and music by Jasper Kyd (a veteran of the Hitman series).", "hours": 35.3, "username": "UthersonL", "products": 1279, "early_access": false}
