{"product_id": "33230", "page": 485, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-09-07", "text": "The social backdrop of Assassin\u2019s Creed II is the birth of modern Europe (in philosophy, engineering, architecture, art, commerce), i.e. the renaissance in northern Italy, that marked the beginning of the end to religious rule. Rapped up in an action packed freerunning/parkour form factor, Assassin\u2019s Creed should appeal to any adrenalin seeking gamer with a taste for beauty and history.", "hours": 86.6, "user_id": "76561197976796645", "username": "w1ntermute", "products": 140, "early_access": false}
