{"product_id": "33230", "page": 486, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-08-10", "text": "Ah, I love this game. I thought I'd pick it up again to see if it still held a place in my heart. I played for a few minutes and fell in love all over again. It's such a pretty game, with a great story, great visuals and wonderful characters.", "hours": 3.5, "username": "Ace de Ignis", "products": 263, "early_access": false}
