{"product_id": "33230", "page": 487, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-08-08", "text": "In Assassin's Creed 2, you play as Easymac Audiotorah, the superjew.  WIth more weapons than the first one, and the addition of upgrades and a currency system, you will be much better at being a superjew than in assassin's creed 1.\n9/10, would allow to charge me interest (and not blame for plagues).", "hours": 22.6, "username": "Camelith", "products": 470, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 487, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-08-08", "text": "Well, this one has cool horses, cool story, nice gameplay and tons of side mission. I think is the best of the serie.\nSCORE: 88/100", "hours": 28.8, "username": "Sherlock Van Helsing", "products": 756, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 487, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-08-06", "text": "Fantastic game, better than Assassins Creed I in that there's more to do. Plus most of the annoyances of previous game have also been removed, whilst retaining much of the good content and developing more of a story focus than the previous title.", "hours": 28.9, "username": "darrensilk3", "products": 187, "early_access": false}
