{"product_id": "33230", "page": 488, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-07-24", "text": "Awesome... , from where should i start , perfect graphics ,  parkour , action , questing , sound , controls , and a story that will get your mind blown , totally A ''must to have'' game 10/10.", "hours": 28.2, "username": "Salah", "products": 460, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 488, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-07-23", "text": "Assassin's Creed II offers a lot of gameplay and will keep you entertained for hours, the story is beautiful, the play style as well, overall better than the first Assassin's creed, of course you've to play the first one to understand the playthrough.\nWhat's also good but interests me the less is the graphics, they're pretty great.\nI give it a 4/5.", "hours": 27.4, "user_id": "76561198045598071", "username": "Mr. Evasive Pants", "products": 258, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 488, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-07-22", "text": "Assassin's Creed II takes all the good bits of the first game and improves on them, while simultaneously integrating many new gameplay elements and quality of life changes. This is the best of the Assassin's Creed series.", "hours": 0.7, "username": "Gilded Phoenix", "products": 183, "early_access": false}
