{"product_id": "33230", "page": 493, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-06-04", "text": "This is my first ever Assassin's Creed game I've ever played and man I wasn't disapointed . For Starters , You had to start at the very beginning of how a young rich playboy found out that he has a long lineage of skilled Assassin's protecting the world from the plan's of the Templars .\nthe one thing that is most Unique about this specific AC Game , is the story and the little comedy relief of it that makes it have its own charm to it . besides all the side quest and collecting all the items to get special stuff , you will enjoy all the fine details and info about the history of Florence and Venice in Renasaince Italy .", "hours": 27.6, "username": "IamBirdman", "products": 146, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 493, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-06-02", "text": "One of my favourite Games of all time. This mainly relies on the great atmosphere created, sucking you into 15th century Italy. The story is solid, with no special twists, but seems realistic and can offer great characters, before all, Ezio himself. Gameplay is fun, you can spend ages just running on the roofs of venice and firenze. Combat is just a bit too easy if you just wait for the right moment to counter-kill, but if you just decide to try to make it hard yourself, it can be fun too. First Playthrough took me around 60h (much of it just random free-roaming). Both, Controller and Keyboard work very well here.", "hours": 204.1, "username": "Burges", "products": 1127, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 493, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-05-31", "text": "\u0412\u0441\u0435 \u043d\u0438\u043a\u0430\u043a \u043d\u0435 \u043c\u043e\u0433 \u043f\u043e\u0438\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0442\u044c \u0438\u0437\u0437\u0430 \u0442\u043e\u0433\u043e \u0447\u0442\u043e \u0441\u0442\u043e\u044f\u043b\u0430 \u0437\u0430\u0449\u0438\u0442\u0430 \u043e\u0442 \u043f\u0438\u0440\u0430\u0442\u043e\u043a, \u0430 \u0432\u0437\u043b\u043e\u043c\u0430\u0442\u044c \u043d\u0435\u043c\u043e\u0433. \u0412\u043e\u0442 \u0431\u044b\u043b\u0430 \u0441\u043a\u0438\u0434\u043a\u0430, 75 \u0440\u0443\u0431\u043b\u0435\u0439 \u0438\u0433\u0440\u0430 \u0441\u0442\u043e\u0438\u043b\u0430, \u043a\u0443\u043f\u0438\u043b, \u043f\u043e\u0438\u0433\u0440\u0430\u043b, \u0440\u0430\u0434.", "hours": 49.9, "username": "Vitok", "products": 373, "early_access": false}
