{"product_id": "33230", "page": 493, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-05-20", "text": "Do you like climbing buildings, stabbing people and being a general badass? Assassin's Creed II does that. I normally don't dig stuff with stealth elements, but this allows you to be stealthy, to fight while telling a fairly interesting story.", "hours": 181.2, "username": "serenyty", "products": 729, "early_access": false}
