{"product_id": "33230", "page": 494, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-04-29", "text": "The Good :\n+ A whole new improvement to the first game\n+ New Ancestor\n+ Cool set of equipments\n+ New Assassination techniques\nThe Bad :\n- Character textures are dull\n- Some Gameplay mechanics are better in it's predecessor\n- A permanent internet connection is required to play the game\n- Dialogues lack depth\n- Pistol shooting and reloading takes time", "hours": 31.9, "username": "Watch_Doge", "products": 143, "early_access": false}
