{"product_id": "33230", "page": 495, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-04-25", "text": "Ubisoft greatly redeems their reputation after the first AC's dismal execution and mundane content. AC2 opens up the world with enough variety and tasks to make it epic, evolving, and welcoming for each session of play. Much praise deserved.", "hours": 43.0, "user_id": "76561198052969087", "username": "Deez", "products": 627, "early_access": false}
