{"product_id": "33230", "page": 497, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-03-22", "text": "Assassin\u2019s Creed II is a gem, a truly masterpiece. Developing a new economic system, and bringing more attention to combats, notoriety and context-script, Ubisoft achieves an awesome and epic experience. This sequel is far better than the first one.\nJust Get it and play the Series.", "hours": 8.7, "username": "S\u1d31\u1d3a\u1d40\u1d35\u1d3a\u1d31\u1d38", "products": 445, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 497, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-03-20", "text": "MUCH better than the first game! Although it feels pretty clunky sometimes and is still a little repetative/tedious, I had a LOT of fun playing this through to the end. Travelling all across Italy, climbing across gorgeous churches and tombs, a much more satisfying final boss fight, but yet another confusing ending xD I'm sure it will all be explained in the next games!\n8/10", "hours": 55.9, "username": "HisEvenSeven", "products": 565, "early_access": false}
