{"product_id": "33230", "page": 497, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-03-19", "text": "I never was a huge fan of the whole open-world GTA thing. After playing this, I found it to provide much fun, although it's a little overrated. The characters and story are interesting at least, bravely taking place over the course of several years. However, the whole revenge aspect grows a bit redundant over time and you'll find yourself doing the same tasks over and over. But give it a try, it's still worth the money!", "hours": 34.9, "user_id": "76561198041644725", "username": "76561198041644725", "products": 196, "early_access": false}
