{"product_id": "33230", "page": 502, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-01-08", "text": "The 2nd game of the franchise and it is a huge step up from the first game. It has added more gameplay features and fighting moves.\nThe storytelling is great and keeps you playing. The characters are very memorable and interesting.\nThe cinematics, graphics and sounds are all great in telling this story.\nA must-buy IP for all gamers.", "hours": 42.9, "user_id": "76561198010479045", "username": "Peter Pan", "products": 176, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 502, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-01-06", "text": "This tale of young ezio bring so much memories back when i beat this game on xbox...\nThe music is just grand, gameplay brought the series to a whole new level.\nWay better than it's ancestor Assassin's Creed.\nControls on PC take a little getting used to, but you can always change your bindings.\nA part of my heart belongs to this series, and half of that part belongs to Assassin's Creed 2...\nThis is a MUST buy.", "hours": 10.1, "username": "Dr.Shmoop", "products": 261, "early_access": false}
