{"product_id": "33230", "page": 503, "page_order": 8, "recommended": false, "date": "2013-01-01", "text": "I will not be purchasing any more of the Assasin's Creed games for the PC.\nIn order to play this, you must run UPLAY (another Steam clone, produced by Ubisoft) at the same time as Steam. Although I could live with that, what's worse is that the keyboard controls are awkward as hell. Atop that, when I attempted to use my Razer Onza [Tournament Edition] in order to play comfortably, it mapped the buttons incorrectly, AND didn't recognize either trigger.\nI emplore you, do not purchase this on PC. Get an XBOX if you really want to play this game that badly, because you'll not enjoy it for PC.", "hours": 0.3, "username": "Slaughter", "products": 279, "early_access": false}
