{"product_id": "33230", "page": 526, "page_order": 5, "recommended": false, "date": "2012-01-04", "text": "a sequel... none of a kind which are match the original well. It has become larger?\n. It has more action?\n. Lots of fun, you know. But, truth to be told,\nand\nare very different games, and I do appreciate the original much more than its sequel. Sometimes I even ask myself: \"hey, am I playing\nnow? No, wait! It's\n!\" -and that's what is really sad.", "hours": 28.7, "username": "(GoR)Andrew.zhd", "products": 353, "early_access": false}
