{"product_id": "33230", "page": 526, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2012-01-02", "text": "One of the greatest games I ever played. Great storyline (Ezzio 5+, Desmond and stuff was interesting only in the very end), fantastic gameplay (yes, Bbatman, you have to learn a thing or 2 from this game), visuals - ok. You'll visit lots of cool places and very extravagant one in the very finale. I strongly recommend you all to play in this marvelous art work! 9.5 / 10!", "hours": 22.7, "username": "\u30a2\u30ec\u30af\u30b5\u30f3\u30c0\u30fc", "products": 688, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 526, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2012-01-02", "text": "Assassin's Creed 2 is a really well-made game just like its predecessor - AC1. Gripping story, insane death blows, and joys of jumping from roof top to roof top. However, the keyboard and mouse controls are awful. Unless you have a gamepad handy, I wouldn't recommend the grab.", "hours": 28.4, "username": "Ult", "products": 427, "early_access": false}
