{"product_id": "33230", "page": 528, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2011-12-28", "text": "A much better improvement over the first game in many areas.  The first game was fun the first few assassinations, but that sensation died off pretty quick.  I had actually quit the first game and didn't finish it until I picked #2 up.  I think we come to realize early on as to whether or not we are AC fans... if the first installment appeared to have a whole lot of potential, but fell short then I don't think you can go wrong by giving it another shot.\nP.S. This is one of very few games out there where I spent over 45 hours playing.", "hours": 72.2, "username": "agedblade", "products": 540, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 528, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2011-12-28", "text": "One of my favorite titles ever, its the closest you weill eve be able to travel in renessaince Italy, must have!", "hours": 48.7, "username": "Gojira", "products": 160, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 528, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2011-12-28", "text": "Assassin's Creed 2 does, like its predecessor, a fantastic job depicting real historical locations and creating a deep level of immersion. It never gets boring since there are many things to do in this game, many locations to explore and quests to complete. The story however is a bit disappointing (not unlike AC1), but it is still a great game worth playing.", "hours": 30.8, "username": "GamingAsArt", "products": 296, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 528, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2011-12-28", "text": "Very easy for anyone to pickup the controller and instantly begin jumping across rooftops with ease, but still allows room to learn and improve. The story is great and hunting for treasure and feathers is also a lot of fun. Recommend using the Xbox 360 controller for PC to play this one.", "hours": 55.2, "username": "Patrick", "products": 4789, "early_access": false}
