{"product_id": "33230", "page": 541, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2011-07-03", "text": "Play the first game! Only then will you appreciate the additions this sequel made. It's a fantastic game, with better gameplay than the original, while following the story arc fluidly. An excellent second chapter in this trilogy (Brotherhood aside). Well worth the money, and time!", "hours": 51.3, "user_id": "76561197993432994", "username": "GoldSabre", "products": 241, "early_access": false}
