{"product_id": "33230", "page": 552, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2010-12-23", "text": "A vast improvement over the first Assassin's Creed.", "hours": 23.4, "username": "Eck", "products": 189, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "33230", "page": 552, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2010-12-20", "text": "Much better than the first, with more variety in everything. If you're the items junkie type, you'll get plenty. The story is interesting but I didn't like the ending much. The gameplay however is improved and the combat mechanics are one of the most fun aspects of the game and one of the best i've seen.\nI'd recommend it but for those with internet D/C issues stay away from it as the game will not continue without an active internet connection at all times.", "hours": 32.5, "user_id": "76561198007296033", "username": "Damnatio Memoriae", "products": 81, "early_access": false}
